      "安全/dotenv: block runtime-控制 env vars plus browser-控制 覆盖 and 跳过-服务器 env vars from untrusted workspace `.env` files, and reject unsafe 链接-style browser 控制 覆盖 specifiers before lazy 加载中. (#62660, #62663) Thanks @eleqtrizit.",
      "Gateway/node exec events: mark remote node `exec.started`, `exec.完成`, and `exec.denied` summaries as untrusted 系统 events and sanitize node-provided command/输出/reason text before enqueueing them, so remote node 输出 cannot inject trusted `系统:` content into later turns. (#62659) Thanks @eleqtrizit.",
