      "Codex CLI: pass OpenClaw's 系统 prompt through Codex's `model_instructions_file` 配置 覆盖 so fresh Codex CLI sessions receive the same prompt g界面dance as Claude CLI sessions.",
      "认证/profiles: persist explicit 认证-profile upserts directly and 跳过 external CLI sync for local writes so profile changes are saved without stale external credential state.",
      "Agents/timeouts: make the LLM idle timeout inherit `agents.defaults.timeoutSeconds` when configured, 禁用 the unconfigured idle watchdog for cron runs, and point idle-timeout errors at `agents.defaults.llm.idleTimeoutSeconds`. Thanks @drvoss.",
      "Agents/failover: classify Z.ai vendor code `1311` as billing and `1113` as auth, including long wrapped `1311` payloads, so these errors stop falling through to generic failover handling. (#49552) Thanks @1bcMax.",
      "QQBot/media-tags: 支持 HTML entity-encoded angle brackets (`&lt;`/`&gt;`), 链接 slashes in attributes, and self-closing media tags so upstream `<qqimg>` payloads are correctly parsed and normalized. (#60493) Thanks @ylc0919.",
