    "features": [
      "CLI/infer: 添加 a 第一个-class `openclaw infer ...` hub for provider-backed inference workflows across model, media, web, and embedding tasks. Thanks @Takhoffman.",
      "Tools/media generation: auto-fallback across 认证-backed 镜像, music, and video providers by default, preserve intent during provider switches, remap 大小/aspect/resolution/duration hints to the closest 支持ed 选项, and surface provider capabilities plus 模式-aware video-to-video 支持.",
      "Memory/wiki: 恢复 the bundled `memory-wiki` stack with 插件, CLI, sync/query/apply tooling, memory-host 集成, structured claim/evidence fields, compiled digest retrieval, claim-health linting, contradiction clustering, staleness dashboards, and freshness-weighted 搜索. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "插件s/webhooks: 添加 a bundled webhook ingress 插件 so external automation can 创建 and drive bound TaskFlows through per-route shared-secret endpoints. (#61892) Thanks @mbelinky.",
      "Gateway/sessions: 添加 persisted compaction checkpoints plus Sessions 界面 branch/恢复 actions so operators can inspect and recover pre-compaction 会话 state. (#62146) Thanks @scoootscooob.",
      "Compaction: 添加 pluggable compaction provider registry so 插件s can 替换 the b界面lt-in summarization pipeline. Configure via `agents.defaults.compaction.provider`; falls 返回 to LLM summarization on provider failure. (#56224) Thanks @DhruvBhatia0.",
      "Agents/系统 prompt: 添加 `agents.defaults.systemPromptOverride` for controlled prompt experiments plus heartbeat prompt-section controls so heartbeat runtime behavior can stay enabled without injecting heartbeat instructions every turn.",
      "Providers/Google: 添加 Gemma 4 model 支持 and keep Google fallback resolution on the requested provider 路径 so native Google Gemma routes work again. (#61507) Thanks @eyjohn.",
      "Providers/Google: preserve explicit thinking-off semantics for Gemma 4 while still enabling Gemma reasoning 支持 in 兼容性 wrappers. (#62127) Thanks @romgenie.",
      "Providers/Arcee AI: 添加 a bundled Arcee AI provider 插件 with Trinity catalog entries, OpenRouter 支持, and 更新d onboarding/认证 g界面dance. (#62068) Thanks @arthurbr11.",
      "Providers/Anthropic: 恢复 Claude CLI as the preferred local Anthropic 路径 in onboarding, model-认证 g界面dance, doctor flows, and Docker Claude CLI live lanes again.",
      "Providers/Ollama: detect vision capability from the `/API/显示` response and set 镜像 输入框 on models that 支持 it so Ollama vision models accept 镜像 attachments. (#62193) Thanks @BruceMacD.",
      "Memory/dreaming: ingest redacted 会话 transcripts into the dreaming corpus with per-day 会话-corpus notes, cursor checkpointing, and promotion/doctor 支持. (#62227) Thanks @vignesh07.",
      "Providers/inferrs: 添加 string-content 兼容性 for stricter OpenAI-compatible chat backends, document `inferrs` setup with a full 配置 example, and 添加 troubleshooting g界面dance for local backends that pass direct probes but fail on full agent-runtime prompts.",
      "Agents/context engine: expose prompt-cache runtime context to context engines and keep current-turn prompt-cache usage aligned with the active attempt instead of stale prior-turn assistant state. (#62179) Thanks @jalehman.",
      "插件 SDK/上下文 engines: pass `availableTools` and `citationsMode` into `assemble()`, and expose memory-artifact and memory-prompt seams so companion 插件s and non-legacy 上下文 engines can consume 激活 memory state without reaching into internals. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "ACP/ACPX 插件: bump the bundled `acpx` pin to `0.5.1` so 插件-local installs and strict version checks pick up the latest published runtime release. (#62148) Thanks @onutc.",
      "Discord/events: allow `event-create` to accept a cover image URL or local file path, load and validate PNG/JPG/GIF event cover media, and pass the encoded image payload through Discord admin action/runtime paths. (#60883) Thanks @bittoby."
    ],
    "improvements": [],
    "bugfixes": [
      "CLI/infer: keep provider-backed infer behavior aligned with actual runtime execution by 修复ing explicit TTS 覆盖 handling, profile-aware gateway TTS prefs resolution, per-request transcription `prompt`/`language` overrides, 镜像 输出 MIME/extension mismatches, configured web-搜索 fallback behavior, and agent-vs-CLI web-搜索 execution drift.",
      "插件s/media: when `插件s.允许` is set, capability fallback now merges bundled capability 插件 ids into the allowlist (not only `插件s.entries`), so media understanding providers such as OpenAI-compatible STT 加载 for voice transcription without req界面ring `openai` in `插件s.允许`. (#62205) Thanks @neeravmakwana.",
      "Agents/history and replies: buffer phaseless OpenAI WS text until a real assistant phase arrives, keep replay and SSE history sequence tracking aligned, 隐藏 commentary and leaked 工具 XML from 用户-可见 history, and keep history-based 关注-向上 replies on `final_answer` text only. (#61729, #61747, #61829, #61855, #61954) Thanks @100yenadmin and contributors.",
      "控制 界面: 显示 `/tts` audio replies in webchat, detect mistaken `?token=` 认证 links with the 正确 `#token=` hint, and keep Copy, Canvas, and 移动端 exec-approval 界面 from covering chat content on narrow screens. (#54842, #61514, #61598) Thanks @neeravmakwana.",
      "iOS/gateway: 替换 string-matched 连接 错误 界面 with structured gateway 连接 problems, preserve actionable pairing/认证 failures over later generic 断开连接 noise, and surface reusable problem banners and details across onboarding, settings, and root 状态 surfaces. (#62650) Thanks @ngutman.",
      "T界面: route `/状态` through the shared 会话-状态 command, keep commentary 隐藏 in history, strip raw envelope metadata from async command notices, preserve fallback streaming before per-attempt failures finalize, and 恢复 Kitty keyboard state on 退出 or fatal crashes. (#49130, #59985, #60043, #61463) Thanks @biefan and contributors.",
      "iOS/Watch exec approvals: keep Apple Watch review and approval 恢复 working while the iPhone is locked or backgrounded, including reconnect 恢复, 待处理 approval persistence, 通知 cleanup, and APNs-backed watch 刷新 恢复. (#61757) Thanks @ngutman.",
      "Agents/上下文 overflow: combine oversized and aggregate 工具-result 恢复 in one pass and 恢复 a total-上下文 overflow backstop so recoverable sessions retry instead of failing early. (#61651) Thanks @Takhoffman.",
      "认证/OpenAI Codex OAuth: 重新加载 fresh on-disk credentials inside the locked 刷新 路径 and retry once after `refresh_token_reused` rotates only the stored 刷新 token, so relogin/restart 恢复 stops getting stuck on stale cached 认证 state. Thanks @owen-ever.",
      "认证/OpenAI Codex OAuth: keep native `/model ...@profile` selections on the target 会话 and honor explicit 用户-locked 认证 profiles even when per-agent 认证 order excludes them. (#62744) Thanks @jalehman.",
      "Providers/Anthropic: preserve thinking blocks for Claude Opus 4.5+, Sonnet 4.5+, and newer Claude 4-family models so prompt-cache pre修复es keep matching, and 跳过 `service_tier` injection on OAuth-authenticated stream wrapper requests so Claude OAuth streaming stops failing with HTTP 401. (#60356, #61793)",
      "Agents/Claude CLI: surface nested API 错误 messages from structured CLI 输出 so billing/认证/provider failures 显示 the real provider 错误 instead of an opaque CLI failure.",
      "Agents/exec: preserve explicit `host=node` routing under elevated defaults when `tools.exec.host=auto`, fail loud on 无效 elevated cross-host overrides, and keep `strictInlineEval` commands blocked after approval timeouts instead of falling through to automatic execution. (#61739) Thanks @obviyus.",
      "Nodes/exec approvals: keep `host=node` POSIX transport shell wrappers (`/bin/sh -lc ...`) aligned with inner-command allowlist analysis so allowlisted scripts 停止 prompting unnecessarily, while Windows `cmd.exe` wrapper runs stay approval-gated. (#62401) Thanks @ngutman.",
      "Nodes/exec approvals: keep Windows `cmd.exe /c` wrapper runs approval-gated even when `env` carriers, including env-assignment carriers, wrap the shell invocation. (#62439) Thanks @ngutman.",
      "Gateway 工具/exec 配置: block model-facing `gateway 配置.apply` and `配置.patch` writes from changing exec approval paths such as `safeBins`, `safeBinProfiles`, `safeBinTrustedDirs`, and `strictInlineEval`, while still allowing unchanged structured values through. (#62001) Thanks @eleqtrizit.",
      "Host exec/env sanitization: block dangerous Java, Rust, Cargo, Git, Kubernetes, cloud credential, 配置-路径, and Helm env overrides so host-运行 tools cannot be redirected to attacker-chosen code, 配置, credentials, or repository state. (#59119, #62002, #62291) Thanks @eleqtrizit and contributors.",
      "Commands/allowlist: req界面re owner 授权 for `/allowlist 添加` and `/allowlist 移除` before channel resolution, so non-owner but command-authorized senders can no longer persistently rewrite allowlist policy state. (#62383) Thanks @pgondhi987.",
      "Feishu/docx uploads: honor `tools.fs.workspaceOnly` for local `upload_file` and `upload_image` paths by forwarding workspace-constrained `localRoots` into the media loader, so docx uploads can no longer read host-local files outside the workspace when workspace-only 模式 is 激活. (#62369) Thanks @pgondhi987.",
      "网络/fetch guard: drop request bodies and body-describing headers on cross-origin `307` and `308` redirects by default, so attacker-controlled redirect hops cannot receive secret-bearing POST payloads from SSRF-guarded fetch flows unless a caller explicitly opts in. (#62357) Thanks @pgondhi987.",
      "Browser/SSRF: treat main-frame `document` redirect hops as navigations even when Playwright does not flag them as `isNavigationRequest()`, so strict private-网络 blocking still stops forbidden redirect pivots before the browser reaches the internal target. (#62355) Thanks @pgondhi987.",
      "Browser/node invoke: block persistent browser profile 创建, 重置, and 删除 mutations through `browser.proxy` on both gateway-forwarded `node.invoke` and the node-host proxy 路径, even when no profile allowlist is configured. (#60489)",
      "Gateway/node pairing: req界面re a fresh pairing request when a previously paired node reconnects with 添加itional declared commands, and keep the live 会话 pinned to the earlier approved command set until the upgrade is approved. (#62658) Thanks @eleqtrizit.",
      "Gateway/认证: invalidate existing shared-token and password WebSocket sessions when the configured secret rotates, so stale authenticated sockets cannot stay attached after token or password changes. (#62350) Thanks @pgondhi987.",
      "MS Teams/安全: validate 文件-consent upload URLs against HTTPS, Microsoft/SharePoint host allowlists, and private-IP DNS checks before uploading attachments, blocking SSRF-style consent-upload abuse. (#23596)",
      "Media/base64 decode guards: enforce byte limits before decoding missed base64-backed Teams, Signal, QQ Bot, and 镜像-工具 payloads so oversized inbound media and 数据 URLs no longer 绕过 pre-decode 大小 checks. (#62007) Thanks @eleqtrizit.",
      "Runtime event trust: mark 背景 `notifyOnExit` summaries, ACP parent-stream relays, and wake-hook payloads as untrusted 系统 events so lower-trust runtime 输出 no longer re-enters later turns as trusted `系统:` text. (#62003)",
      "Auto-reply/media: 允许 managed generated-media `MEDIA:` paths from normal reply text again while still blocking arbitrary host-local media and document paths, so generated media keep delivering without reopening host-路径 injection holes.",
      "Gateway/状态 and containers: auto-绑定 to `0.0.0.0` inside Docker and Podman environments, and probe local TLS gateways over `wss://` with self-signed fingerprint forwarding so 容器 startup and loopback TLS 状态 checks work again. (#61818, #61935) Thanks @openperf and contributors.",
      "Gateway/OpenAI-compatible HTTP: 中止 in-flight `/v1/chat/completions` and `/v1/responses` turns when clients 断开连接 so abandoned HTTP requests 停止 wasting agent runtime. (#54388) Thanks @Lellansin.",
      "macOS/gateway 版本: strip trailing commit metadata from CLI 版本 输出 before semver parsing so the Mac 应用 recognizes installed gateway versions 点赞 `OpenClaw 2026.4.2 (d74a122)` again. (#61111) Thanks @oliviareid-svg.",
      "Sessions/model selection: resolve the explicitly 选中 会话 model separately from runtime fallback resolution so 会话 状态 and live model switching stay aligned with the chosen model.",
      "Discord/ACP bindings: canonicalize DM conversation identity across inbound messages, 组件 interactions, native commands, and current-conversation binding resolution so `--绑定 here` in Discord DMs keeps routing 关注-向上 replies to the bound agent instead of falling 返回 to the default agent.",
      "Discord: recover forwarded referenced 消息 text and attachments when snapshots are missing, use `ws://` again for gateway 监控 sockets, 停止 forcing a hardcoded temperature for Codex-backed auto-thread titles, and harden voice receive 恢复 so rAPId speaker restarts keep their 下一个 utterance. (#41536, #61670) Thanks @artwalker and contributors.",
      "Slack/thread mentions: 添加 `channels.slack.thread.req界面reExplicitMention` so Slack channels that already req界面re mentions can also req界面re explicit `@bot` mentions inside bot-participated threads. (#58276) Thanks @praktika-engineer.",
      "Slack/threading: keep legacy thread stickiness for real replies when older callers omit `isThreadReply`, while still honoring `replyToMode` for Slack's auto-created 顶部-level `thread_ts`. (#61835) Thanks @kaonash.",
      "Slack/media: keep attachment downloads on the SSRF-guarded dispatcher 路径 so Slack media fetching works on Node 22 without dropping pinned transport enforcement. (#62239) Thanks @openperf.",
      "Matrix/onboarding: 添加 an invite auto-连接 setup step with explicit off warnings and strict 稳定-target validation so 新增 Matrix accounts 停止 silently ignoring invited rooms and fresh DM-style invites unless operators opt in. (#62168) Thanks @gumadeiras.",
      "Matrix/formatting: preserve multi-paragraph and loose-列表 rendering in Element so numbered and bulleted Markdown keeps their content attached to the 正确 列表 项目. (#60997) Thanks @gucasbrg.",
      "Telegram/doctor: keep 顶部-level 访问-控制 fallback in place during multi-账户 normalization while still promoting legacy default 认证 into `accounts.default`, so existing named bots keep inherited allowlists without dropping the legacy default bot. (#62263) Thanks @obviyus.",
      "插件s/loaders: centralize bundled `dist/**` Jiti native-加载 policy and keep channel, public-surface, facade, and 配置-metadata loader seams off native Jiti on Windows so onboarding and configure flows 停止 tripping `ERR_UN支持ED_ESM_URL_SCHEME`. (#62286) Thanks @chen-zhang-cs-code.",
      "插件s/channels: keep bundled channel artifact and secret-contract 加载中 稳定 under lazy 加载中, preserve 插件-schema defaults during 安装, and 修复 Windows `文件://` plus native-Jiti 插件 loader paths so onboarding, doctor, `openclaw secret`, and bundled 插件 installs work again. (#61832, #61836, #61853, #61856) Thanks @Zeesejo and contributors.",
      "插件s/ClawHub: verify downloaded 插件 archives against 版本 metadata SHA-256, fail closed when 归档 integrity metadata is missing or malformed, and tighten fallback ZIP verification so 插件 installs cannot proceed on mismatched or incomplete ClawHub package metadata. (#60517) Thanks @mappel-nv.",
      "插件s/provider hooks: 停止 recursive provider snapshot loads from overflowing the stack during 插件 initialization, while still preserving cached nested provider-hook results. (#61922, #61938, #61946, #61951)",
      "Docker/插件s: 停止 forcing bundled 插件 discovery to `/应用/extensions` in runtime images so packaged installs use compiled `dist/extensions` artifacts again and Node 24 containers do not boot through source-only 插件 entry paths. 修复es #62044. (#62316) Thanks @gumadeiras.",
      "Providers/Ollama: honor the 选中 provider's `baseUrl` during streaming so multi-Ollama setups 停止 routing every stream to the 第一个 configured Ollama endpoint. (#61678)",
      "Providers/Ollama: 停止 警告 that Ollama could not be reached when discovery only sees 空 default local stubs, while still keeping real explicit Ollama overrides loud when the endpoint is unreachable.",
      "Providers/xAI: recognize `API.grok.x.ai` as an xAI-native endpoint again and keep legacy `x_search` 认证 resolution working so older xAI web-搜索 configs 继续 to 加载. (#61377) Thanks @jjjojoj.",
      "Providers/Mistral: send `reasoning_effort` for `mistral/mistral-small-最新` (Mistral Small 4) with thinking-level mapping, and mark the catalog entry as reasoning-capable so adjustable reasoning matches Mistral’s Chat Completions API. (#62162) Thanks @neeravmakwana.",
      "OpenAI TTS/Groq: send `wav` to Groq-compatible speech endpoints, honor explicit `responseFormat` overrides on OpenAI-compatible paths, and only mark voice-note 输出 as voice-compatible when the actual format is `opus`. (#62233) Thanks @neeravmakwana.",
      "Tools/web_fetch and web_search: 修复 `TypeError: fetch failed` caused by undici 8.0 enabling HTTP/2 by default; pinned SSRF-guard dispatchers now explicitly set `allowH2: false` to 恢复 HTTP/1.1 behavior and keep the custom DNS-pinning lookup compatible. (#61738, #61777) Thanks @zozo123.",
      "Tools/web 搜索/Exa: 显示 Exa 搜索 in onboarding and configure provider pickers again by marking the bundled Exa provider as setup-可见. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Memory/vector recall: surface explicit warnings when `sqlite-vec` is unavailable or vector writes are degraded, and strip managed Light Sleep and REM blocks before daily-note ingestion so memory indexing and dreaming 停止 reporting false-成功 or re-ingesting staged 输出. (#61720) Thanks @MonkeyLeeT.",
      "Memory/dreaming: make Dreams config reads and writes respect the selected memory slot 插件 instead of always targeting `memory-core`. (#62275) Thanks @SnowSky1.",
      "QQ Bot/media: route gateway-side attachment and fallback downloads through guarded QQ/Tencent HTTPS fetches so QQ media handling no longer follows arbitrary remote hosts.",
      "Browser/remote CDP: retry the DevTools websocket once after remote browser restarts so healthy remote browser profiles do not fail availability checks during CDP warm-向上. (#57397) Thanks @ThanhNguyxn07.",
      "界面/light 模式: target both root and nested WebKit scrollbar thumbs in the light theme so 页面-level and 容器 scrollbars stay 可见 on light backgrounds. (#61753) Thanks @chziyue.",
      "Agents/subagents: honor `sessions_spawn(lightContext: true)` for spawned subagent runs by preserving lightweight bootstrap 上下文 through the gateway and embedded runner instead of silently falling 返回 to full workspace bootstrap injection. (#62264) Thanks @theSamPadilla.",
      "Cron: 加载 `jobId` into `id` when the on-disk store omits `id`, matching doctor migration and 修复ing `unknown cron job id` for hand-edited `jobs.json`. (#62246) Thanks @neeravmakwana.",
      "Agents/model fallback: classify minimal HTTP 404 API errors (for example `404 状态 code (no body)`) as `model_not_found` so assistant failures throw into the fallback chain instead of stopping at the 第一个 fallback candidate. (#62119) Thanks @neeravmakwana.",
      "BlueBubbles/网络: respect explicit private-网络 opt-out for loopback and private `serverUrl` values across 账户 resolution, 状态 probes, 监控 startup, and attachment downloads, while keeping public-host attachment hostname pinning intact. (#59373) Thanks @jpreagan.",
      "Agents/heartbeat: keep heartbeat runs pinned to the main 会话 so 激活 subagent transcripts are not overwritten by heartbeat 状态 messages. (#61803) Thanks @100yenadmin.",
      "Agents/heartbeat: respect 禁用 heartbeat prompt g界面dance so operators can suppress heartbeat prompt instructions without disabling heartbeat runtime behavior.",
      "Agents/compaction: 停止 compaction-wait aborts from re-entering prompt failover and replaying completed 工具 turns. (#62600) Thanks @i-dentifier.",
      "Approvals/runtime: move native approval lifecycle assembly into shared core bootstrap/runtime seams driven by channel capabilities and runtime contexts, and 移除 the legacy bundled approval fallback wiring. (#62135) Thanks @gumadeiras.",
      "安全/fetch-guard: 停止 rejecting operator-configured proxy hostnames against the target-scoped hostname allowlist in SSRF-guarded fetches, restoring proxy-based media downloads for Telegram and other channels. (#62312) Thanks @ademczuk.",
      "Logging: make `logging.level` and `logging.consoleLevel` honor the documented severity threshold ordering again, and keep child loggers inheriting the parent `minLevel`. (#44646) Thanks @zhumengzhu.",
      "Agents/sessions_send: pass `threadId` through announce delivery so cross-会话 notifications land in the 正确 Telegram forum topic instead of the group's general thread. (#62758) Thanks @jalehman.",
      "Daemon/systemd: keep sudo systemctl calls scoped to the invoking 用户 when machine-scoped systemctl fails, while still avoiding machine fallback for 权限-denied 用户 bus errors. (#62337) Thanks @Aftabbs.",
      "Docs/i18n: relocalize 最终 localized-页面 links after translation and 移除 the zh-CN homepage redirect 覆盖 so localized Mintlify pages resolve to the 正确 language roots again. (#61796) Thanks @hxy91819.",
      "Agents/exec: keep timed-out shell-backgrounded commands on the failed 路径 and point long-running jobs to exec 背景/yield sessions so process polling is only suggested for registered sessions."
    ]
  }
},
  {
  "version": "2026.4.5",
  "date": "2026-04-06",
  "type": "稳定版",
  "latest": false,
  "changes": {
    "features": [
      "Agents/video generation: 添加 the b界面lt-in `video_generate` 工具 so agents can 创建 videos through configured providers and return the generated media directly in the reply.",
      "Agents/music generation: 忽略 un支持ed 可选 hints such as `durationSeconds` with a 警告 instead of hard-failing requests on providers 点赞 Google Lyria.",
      "Providers/Comfy界面: 添加 a bundled `comfy` workflow media 插件 for local Comfy界面 and Comfy Cloud workflows, including shared `image_generate`, `video_generate`, and workflow-backed `music_generate` 支持, with prompt injection, optional reference-image upload, live tests, and output download.",
      "Tools/music generation: 添加 the b界面lt-in `music_generate` 工具 with bundled Google (Lyria) and MiniMax providers plus workflow-backed Comfy 支持, including async task tracking and 关注-向上 delivery of 完成 audio.",
      "Providers: 添加 bundled Qwen, Fireworks AI, and StepFun providers, plus MiniMax TTS, Ollama Web Search, and MiniMax Search 集成s for chat, speech, and search workflows. (#60032, #55921, #59318, #54648)",
      "Providers/Amazon Bedrock: 添加 bundled Mantle 支持 plus inference-profile discovery and automatic request-region injection so Bedrock-hosted Claude, GPT-OSS, Qwen, Kimi, GLM, and similar routes work with less manual setup. (#61296, #61299) Thanks @wirjo.",
      "控制 界面/multilingual: 添加 localized 控制 界面 支持 for Simplified Chinese, Traditional Chinese, Brazilian Portuguese, German, Spanish, Japanese, Korean, French, Turkish, Indonesian, Polish, and Ukrainian. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "插件s: 添加 插件-配置 T界面 prompts to g界面ded onboarding/setup flows, and 添加 `openclaw 插件s 安装 --force` so existing 插件 and hook-pack targets can be replaced without using the dangerous-code 覆盖 flag. (#60590, #60544)",
      "Control 界面/skills: 添加 ClawHub search, detail, and install flows directly in the Skills panel. (#60134) Thanks @samzong.",
      "iOS/exec approvals: 添加 generic APNs approval notifications that 打开 an in-应用 exec approval 模态框, fetch command details only after authenticated operator reconnect, and 清除 stale 通知 state when the approval resolves. (#60239) Thanks @ngutman.",
      "Matrix/exec approvals: 添加 Matrix-native exec approval prompts with 账户-scoped approvers, channel-or-DM delivery, and room-thread aware resolution handling. (#58635) Thanks @gumadeiras.",
      "Channels/上下文 visibility: 添加 configurable `contextVisibility` per channel (`all`, `allowlist`, `allowlist_quote`) so supplemental quote, thread, and fetched history 上下文 can be filtered by sender allowlists instead of always passing through as received.",
      "Providers/request overrides: 添加 shared model and media request transport overrides across OpenAI-, Anthropic-, Google-, and compatible provider paths, including headers, 认证, proxy, and TLS controls. (#60200)",
      "Providers/OpenAI: 添加 前进-compat `openai-codex/gpt-5.4-mini`, an opt-in GPT personality, and provider-owned GPT-5 prompt contributions so Codex/GPT runs stay cache-稳定 and compatible with bundled catalog lag.",
      "Agents/Claude CLI: expose OpenClaw tools to 背景 Claude CLI runs through a loopback MCP bridge and 开关 bundled runs to stdin + `stream-json` partial-消息 streaming so prompts 停止 riding argv, long replies 显示 live 进度, and 最终 会话/usage metadata still land cleanly. (#35676) Thanks @mylukin.",
      "ACPX/runtime: embed the ACP runtime directly in the bundled `acpx` 插件, 移除 the extra external ACP CLI hop, harden live ACP 会话 binding and reuse, and 添加 a generic `reply_dispatch` hook so bundled 插件s 点赞 ACPX can own reply interception without hardcoded ACP paths in core auto-reply routing. (#61319)",
      "Agents/进度: 添加 experimental structured plan 更新s and structured execution 项目 events so compatible 界面s can 显示 clearer step-by-step 进度 during long-running runs.",
      "Providers/Anthropic: 移除 the Claude CLI backend and setup-token from 新增 onboarding, keep existing configured legacy profiles runnable, and have `openclaw doctor` repair or 移除 stale `anthropic:claude-cli` state during migration.",
      "Tools/video generation: 添加 bundled xAI (`grok-imagine-video`), Alibaba Model Studio Wan, and Runway video providers, plus live-测试/default model wiring for all three.",
      "Memory/搜索: 添加 Amazon Bedrock embeddings for Titan, Cohere, Nova, and TwelveLabs models, with AWS credential-chain auto-detection for `provider: \"auto\"` and provider-specific dimension controls. Thanks @wirjo.",
      "Providers/Amazon Bedrock Mantle: generate bearer tokens from the AWS credential chain so Mantle auto-discovery can use IAM 认证 without manually exporting `AWS_BEARER_TOKEN_BEDROCK`. Thanks @wirjo.",
      "Memory/dreaming (experimental): 添加 weighted short-term recall promotion, a `/dreaming` command, Dreams 界面, multilingual conceptual tagging, and doctor/状态 repair 支持, while 重构ing dreaming from competing modes into three cooperative phases (light, deep, REM) with independent schedules and 恢复 behavior so durable memory promotion can 运行 in the 背景 with less manual setup. (#60569, #60697) Thanks @vignesh07.",
      "Memory/dreaming: 添加 configurable aging controls (`recencyHalfLifeDays`, `maxAgeDays`) plus 可选 verbose logging so operators can tune recall decay and inspect promotion decisions more easily.",
      "Memory/dreaming: 添加 REM 预览 tooling (`openclaw memory rem-harness`, `promote-explain`), surface possible lasting truths during REM 预发布, and make deep promotion replay-safe so reruns reconcile instead of duplicating `MEMORY.md` entries.",
      "Memory/dreaming: write dreaming trail content to top-level `dreams.md` instead of daily memory notes, 更新 `/dreaming` help text to point there, and keep `dreams.md` available for explicit reads without pulling it into default recall. Thanks @davemorin.",
      "Memory/dreaming: 添加 the Dream Diary surface in Dreams, simplify user-facing dreaming config to `enabled` plus optional `frequency`, treat phases as 实现ation detail in docs/界面, and keep the lobster animation visible above diary content. Thanks @vignesh07.",
      "Prompt caching: keep prompt pre修复es more reusable across transport fallback, deterministic MCP 工具 ordering, compaction, embedded 镜像 history, normalized 系统-prompt fingerprints, `openclaw 状态 --verbose` cache diagnostics, and the removal of duplicate in-band 工具 inventories from agent 系统 prompts so 关注-向上 turns hit cache more reliably. (#58036, #58037, #58038, #59054, #60603, #60691) Thanks @bcherny and @vincentkoc.",
      "Agents/cache: diagnostics: 添加 prompt-cache 中断 diagnostics, trace live cache scenarios through embedded runner paths, and 显示 cache reuse explicitly in `openclaw 状态 --verbose`. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Agents/cache: stabilize cache-relevant 系统 prompt fingerprints by normalizing eq界面valent structured prompt whitespace, line endings, hook-添加ed 系统 上下文, and runtime capability ordering so semantically unchanged prompts reuse KV/cache more reliably. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Agents/工具 prompts: 移除 the duplicate in-band 工具 inventory from agent 系统 prompts so 工具-calling models rely on the structured 工具 definitions as the single source of truth, improving prompt 稳定性 and reducing stale 工具 g界面dance.",
      "配置/schema: enrich the exported `openclaw 配置 schema` JSON Schema with 字段 titles and descriptions so editors, agents, and other schema consumers receive the same 配置 help metadata. (#60067) Thanks @solavrc.",
      "Providers/CLI: 移除 bundled CLI text-provider backends and the `agents.defaults.cliBackends` surface, while keeping ACP harness sessions and Gemini media understanding on the native bundled providers.",
      "Matrix/exec approvals: clarify unavailable-approval replies so Matrix no longer claims chat approvals are un支持ed when native exec approvals are merely unconfigured. (#61424) Thanks @gumadeiras.",
      "Docs/IRC: 替换 public IRC hostname examples with `irc.example.com` and recommend private servers for bot coordination while listing common public networks for intentional use.",
      "Memory/dreaming: group nearby daily-note lines into short coherent chunks before staging them for dreaming, so one-off context from recent notes reaches REM/deep with better evidence and less line-level noise.",
      "Memory/dreaming: drop generic date/day headings from daily-note chunk pre修复es while keeping meaningful section labels, so staged snippets stay cleaner and more reusable. (#61597) Thanks @mbelinky.",
      "插件s/Lobster: 运行 bundled Lobster workflows in process instead of spawning the external CLI, reducing transport overhead and unblocking native runtime 集成. (#61523) Thanks @mbelinky.",
      "插件s/Lobster: harden managed 恢复 validation so 无效 TaskFlow 恢复 calls fail earlier, and memoize embedded runtime 加载中 per runner while keeping failed loads retryable. (#61566) Thanks @mbelinky."
    ],
    "improvements": [
      "配置: 移除 legacy public 配置 aliases such as `talk.voiceId` / `talk.APIKey`, `agents.*.沙箱.perSession`, `browser.ssrfPolicy.allowPrivateNetwork`, `hooks.internal.handlers`, and channel/group/room `允许` toggles in favor of the canonical public paths and `enabled`, while keeping 加载-time 兼容性 and `openclaw doctor --修复` migration 支持 for existing configs. (#60726) Thanks @vincentkoc."
    ],
    "bugfixes": [
      "安全: preserve restrictive 插件-only 工具 allowlists, req界面re owner 访问 for `/allowlist 添加` and `/allowlist 移除`, fail closed when `before_tool_call` hooks crash, block browser SSRF redirect bypasses earlier, and keep non-interactive 认证-choice inference scoped to bundled and already-trusted 插件s. (#58476, #59836, #59822, #58771, #59120) Thanks @eleqtrizit and @pgondhi987.",
      "Providers/OpenAI: make GPT-5 and Codex runs act sooner with lower-verbosity defaults, visible progress during tool work, and a one-shot retry when a turn only narrates the plan instead of taking action.",
      "Providers/OpenAI and reply delivery: preserve native `reasoning.effort: \"none\"` and strict schemas where 支持ed, 添加 GPT-5.4 assistant `phase` metadata across replay and the Gateway `/v1/responses` layer, and keep commentary buffered until `final_answer` so web chat, 会话 previews, embedded replies, and Telegram partials 停止 leaking planning text. 修复es #59150, #59643, #61282.",
      "Telegram: 修复 current-model checks in the model picker, HTML-format non-default `/model` confirmations, explicit topic replies, persisted reaction ownership across restarts, caption-media 占位符 and `file_id` preservation on download failure, and upgraded-安装 inbound 镜像 reads. (#60384, #60042, #59634, #59207, #59948, #59971) Thanks @sfuminya, @GitZhangChi, @dashhuang, @samzong, @v1p0r, and @neeravmakwana.",
      "Telegram: 恢复 DM voice-note preflight transcription so direct-消息 audio stops arriving as raw `<media:audio>` placeholders. (#61008) Thanks @manueltarouca.",
      "Telegram/reasoning: only 创建 a Telegram reasoning 预览 lane when the 会话 is explicitly `reasoning:stream`, so 隐藏 `<think>` traces from streamed replies 停止 surfacing as chat previews on normal sessions. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Telegram/native command 菜单: trim long 菜单 descriptions before dropping commands so sub-100 command sets can still fit Telegram's payload budget and keep more `/` entries 可见. (#61129) Thanks @neeravmakwana.",
      "Discord: keep REST, webhook, and 监控 traffic on the configured proxy, preserve 组件-only media sends, honor `@everyone` and `@here` mention gates, keep ACK reactions on the 激活 账户, and 拆分 voice 连接/playback timeouts so auto-连接 is more reliable. (#57465, #60361, #60345) Thanks @geekhuashan.",
      "Discord/reply tags: strip leaked `[[reply_to_current]]` 控制 tags from 预览 text and honor explicit reply-标签 threading during 最终 delivery, so Discord replies stay attached to the triggering 消息 instead of printing reply metadata into chat.",
      "Discord/replies: 替换 the unshipped `replyToOnlyWhenBatched` flag with `replyToMode: \"batched\"` so native reply references only 附加 on debounced multi-消息 turns while explicit reply tags still work.",
      "Discord/镜像 generation: include the real generated `MEDIA:` paths in 工具 输出, avoid duplicate plain-输出 media requeueing, and persist volatile workspace-generated media into durable outbound media before 最终 reply delivery so generated 镜像 replies 停止 pointing at missing local files.",
      "Slack: route live DM replies 返回 to the concrete inbound DM channel while keeping persisted routing metadata 用户-scoped, so normal assistant replies 停止 disappearing when pairing and 系统 messages still arrive. (#59030) Thanks @afurm.",
      "WhatsApp: 恢复 `channels.whatsapp.blockStreaming` and 重置 watchdog timeouts after reconnect so q界面et chats 停止 falling into reconnect loops. (#60007, #60069) Thanks @MonkeyLeeT and @mcaxtr.",
      "Android/Talk 模式: 取消 in-flight `talk.speak` playback when speech is explicitly stopped, and 恢复 spoken replies on both node-scoped and gateway-backed sessions by keeping reply routing and embedded transport overrides aligned with the current playback 路径. (#60306, #61164, #61214)",
      "Voice-call/OpenAI: pass full 插件 配置 into realtime transcription provider resolution so streaming calls can discover the bundled OpenAI realtime transcription provider again. 修复es #60936. Thanks @sliekens and @vincentkoc.",
      "Matrix/exec approvals: anchor seeded approval reactions to the primary Matrix prompt event, resolve them from event metadata instead of prompt text, and clean 向上 chunked approval prompts correctly. (#60931) Thanks @gumadeiras.",
      "Matrix: recover more reliably when secret storage or 恢复 keys are missing by recreating secret storage during repair and 备份 重置, hold crypto snapshot locks during persistence, and surface explicit too-large attachment markers. (#59846, #59851, #60599, #60289) Thanks @al3mart, @emonty, and @efe-arv.",
      "Matrix/DM sessions: 添加 `channels.matrix.dm.sessionScope`, shared-会话 collision notices, and aligned outbound 会话 reuse so separate Matrix DM rooms can keep distinct 上下文 when configured. (#61373) Thanks @gumadeiras.",
      "Matrix: move legacy 顶部-level `avatarUrl` into the default 账户 during multi-账户 promotion and keep env-backed 账户 setup avatar 配置 persisted. (#61437) Thanks @gumadeiras.",
      "MS Teams: download inline DM images via Graph API and preserve channel reply threading in proactive fallback. (#52212, #55198) Thanks @Ted-developer and @hyojin.",
      "MS Teams: 替换 the deprecated Teams SDK Http插件 stub with `httpServerAdapter` so recurring gateway deprecation warnings 停止 firing and the Express 5 兼容性 workaround stays on the 支持ed SDK 路径. (#60939) Thanks @coolramukaka-sys.",
      "Control 界面/chat: 添加 a per-session thinking-level picker in the chat header and mobile chat settings, and keep the browser bundle on 界面-local thinking/session-key helpers so Safari no longer crashes on Node-only imports before rendering chat controls.",
      "沙箱/SSH: reject hardlinked files during cross-device rename fallback so EXDEV 文件 copies preserve the same pinned 文件-boundary checks as direct reads.",
      "Control 界面: keep Stop visible during tool-only execution, preserve pending-send busy state, and clear stale ClawHub search results as soon as the query changes. (#54528, #59800, #60267) Thanks @chziyue and @frankekn.",
      "控制 界面/avatar: honor `界面.assistant.avatar` when serving `/avatar/:agentId` so Appearance 界面 avatar paths 停止 falling 返回 to initials placeholders. (#60778) Thanks @hannasdev.",
      "Control 界面/cron: highlight the Cron refresh button while refresh is in flight so the page's loading state stays visible even when prior data remains on screen. (#60394) Thanks @coder-zhuzm.",
      "控制 界面/Overview: 防止 gateway 访问 token/password visibility 切换器 buttons from overlapping their inputs at narrow widths. (#56924) Thanks @bbddbb1.",
      "Auto-reply: unify reply lifecycle ownership across preflight compaction, 会话 rotation, CLI-backed runs, and gateway restart handling so `/停止` and same-会话 overlap checks target the 向右 激活 turn and restart-interrupted turns return the restart notice instead of being silently dropped. (#61267) Thanks @dutifulbob.",
      "Reply delivery: 防止 duplicate block replies on `text_end` channels so providers that emit explicit text-结束 boundaries no longer double-send the same 最终 消息. (#61530)",
      "Gateway/startup: default `gateway.mode` to `local` when unset, detect PID recycling in gateway lock files on Windows and macOS, and show startup progress so healthy restarts stop getting blocked by stale locks. (#54801, #60085, #59843) Thanks @BradGroux and @TonyDerek-dot.",
      "Gateway/macOS: let launchd `KeepAlive` own in-process gateway restarts again, 添加ing a short supervised-退出 delay so rAPId restarts avoid launchd crash-loop unloads while `openclaw gateway restart` still reports real LaunchAgent errors synchronously.",
      "Gateway/macOS: re-bootstrap the LaunchAgent if `launchctl kickstart -k` unloads it during restart so failed restarts do not leave the gateway unmanaged until manual repair.",
      "Gateway/macOS: recover installed-but-unloaded LaunchAgents during `openclaw gateway 开始` and `restart`, while still preferring live unmanaged gateways during restart 恢复. (#43766) Thanks @HenryC-3.",
      "Gateway/Windows scheduled tasks: preserve Task Scheduler settings on reinstall, fail loudly when `/运行` does not 开始, and 报告 fast failed restarts accurately instead of pretending they timed out after 60 seconds. (#59335) Thanks @tmimmanuel.",
      "Windows/restart: fall 返回 to the installed Startup-entry launcher when the scheduled task was never registered, so `/restart` can relaunch the gateway on Windows setups where `schtasks` 安装 fell 返回 during onboarding. (#58943) Thanks @imechZhangLY.",
      "Windows/restart: clean 向上 stale gateway listeners before Windows self-restart and treat listener and argv probe failures as inconclusive, so scheduled-task relaunch no longer falls into an `E添加RINUSE` retry loop. (#60480) Thanks @arifahmedjoy.",
      "更新/npm: prefer the npm binary that owns the installed global OpenClaw pre修复 so mixed Homebrew-plus-nvm setups 更新 the right install. (#60153) Thanks @jayeshp19.",
      "Agents/music and video generation: 添加 `tools.media.asyncCompletion.directSend` as an opt-in direct-delivery 路径 for 完成 async media tasks, while keeping the legacy requester-会话 wake/model-delivery flow as the default.",
      "CLI/skills JSON: route `skills 列表 --json`, `skills 信息 --json`, and `skills check --json` 输出 to stdout instead of stderr so machine-readable consumers receive JSON on the expected stream again. (#60914; 修复es #57599; landed from contributor PR #57611 by @Aftabbs) Thanks @Aftabbs.",
      "CLI/Commander: preserve Commander-computed 退出 codes for argument and help-错误 paths, and cover the 用户-argv parse 模式 in the regression tests so 无效 CLI invocations no longer 报告 成功 when exits are intercepted. (#60923) Thanks @Linux2010.",
      "Cron: replay interrupted recurring jobs on the 第一个 gateway restart instead of 等待中 for a second restart. (#60583) Thanks @joelnishanth.",
      "Cron: send failure notifications through the job's primary delivery channel using the same 会话 上下文 as successful delivery when no explicit `failureDestination` is configured. (#60622) Thanks @artwalker.",
      "Exec/remote skills: 停止 advertising `exec host=node` when the current exec policy cannot route to a node, and clarify blocked exec-host 覆盖 errors with both the requested host and allowed 配置 路径.",
      "Agents/Claude CLI/安全: 清除 inherited Claude Code 配置-root and 插件-root env overrides 点赞 `CLAUDE_CONFIG_DIR` and `CLAUDE_CODE_插件_*`, so OpenClaw-launched Claude CLI runs cannot be silently pointed at an alternate Claude 配置/插件 tree with different hooks, 插件s, or 认证 上下文. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Agents/Claude CLI/安全: 清除 inherited Claude Code provider-routing and managed-认证 env overrides, and mark OpenClaw-launched Claude CLI runs as host-managed, so Claude CLI backdoor sessions cannot be silently redirected to proxy, Bedrock, Vertex, Foundry, or parent-managed token contexts. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Agents/Claude CLI/安全: force host-managed Claude CLI backdoor runs to `--设置-sources 用户`, even under custom backend arg overrides, so repo-local `.claude` project/local settings, hooks, and 插件 discovery do not silently 执行 inside non-interactive OpenClaw sessions. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Agents/Claude CLI: treat malformed bare `--权限-模式` backend overrides as missing and fail safe 返回 to `bypassPermissions`, so custom `cliBackends.claude-cli.args` 安全 配置 cannot accidentally consume the 下一个 flag as a bogus 权限 模式. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Gateway/device pairing: req界面re non-admin paired-device sessions to manage only their own device for token rotate/revoke and paired-device removal, blocking cross-device token theft inside pairing-scoped sessions. (#50627) Thanks @coygeek.",
      "Gateway/插件 routes: keep gateway-认证 插件 runtime routes on write-only fallback scopes unless a trusted-proxy caller explicitly declares narrower `x-openclaw-scopes`, so 插件 HTTP handlers no longer mint 管理员-level runtime scopes on missing or untrusted HTTP scope headers. (#59815) Thanks @pgondhi987.",
      "B界面ld/types: 修复 the Node `createReq界面re(...)` helper typing so provider-runtime lazy loads compile cleanly again and `pnpm b界面ld` no longer fails in the Pi embedded provider error-pattern path.",
