      "Gateway/device 认证: reuse cached device-token scopes only for cached-token reconnects, while keeping explicit `deviceToken` scope requests and 空-cache fallbacks intact so reconnects preserve `operator.read` without breaking explicit 认证 flows. (#46032) Thanks @caicongyang.",
      "移动端 pairing/安全: fail closed for internal `/pair` setup-code issuance, cleanup, and approval paths when gateway pairing scopes are missing, and keep approval-time requested-scope enforcement on the internal command 路径. (#55996) Thanks @coygeek.",
