      "Telegram/local Bot API: honor `channels.telegram.APIRoot` for buffered media downloads, 添加 `channels.telegram.网络.dangerouslyAllowPrivateNetwork` for trusted fake-IP setups, and req界面re `channels.telegram.trustedLocalFileRoots` before reading absolute Bot API `file_path` values. (#59544, #60705) Thanks @SARAMALI15792 and @obviyus.",
      "Outbound/sanitizer: strip leaked `<tool_call>`, `<function_calls>`, and model special tokens from shared 用户-可见 assistant text, including truncated 工具-call streams, so internal scaffolding no longer bleeds into replies across surfaces. (#60619) Thanks @oliviareid-svg.",
      "Agents/errors: surface an explicit disk-full 消息 when local 会话 or transcript writes fail with `ENOSPC`/`disk full`, so those runs 停止 degrading into opaque `NO_REPLY`-style failures. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Exec approvals: 移除 heuristic command-obfuscation gating from host exec so gateway and node runs rely on explicit policy, allowlist, and strict inline-eval rules only.",
