      "Memory: keep `memory-core` b界面ltin embedding registration on the already-registered 路径 so selecting `memory-core` no longer recurses through 插件 discovery and crashes during startup. (#61402) Thanks @ngutman.",
      "Agents/工具 results: keep large `read` outputs 可见 longer, preserve the 最新 `read` 输出 when older 工具 输出 can absorb the overflow budget, and fall 返回 to Pi's normal overflow compaction/retry 路径 before replacing a fresh `read` with a compacted stub. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Memory/QMD: prefer modern `qmd collection 添加 --glob`, accept newer single-line JSON hit metadata while keeping legacy line fields, 刷新 QMD docs/doctor 安装 g界面dance and model-覆盖 g界面dance, and keep older QMD releases working. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "MS Teams: download inline DM images via Graph API and preserve channel reply threading in proactive fallback. (#52212, #55198) Thanks @Ted-developer and @hyojin.",
      "MS Teams: 替换 the deprecated Teams SDK Http插件 stub with `httpServerAdapter` so recurring gateway deprecation warnings 停止 firing and the Express 5 兼容性 workaround stays on the 支持ed SDK 路径. (#60939) Thanks @coolramukaka-sys.",
      "Matrix/exec approvals: anchor seeded approval reactions to the primary Matrix prompt event, resolve them from event metadata instead of prompt text, and clean 向上 chunked approval prompts correctly. (#60931) Thanks @gumadeiras.",
      "Matrix: recover more reliably when secret storage or 恢复 keys are missing by recreating secret storage during repair and 备份 重置, hold crypto snapshot locks during persistence, and surface explicit too-large attachment markers. (#59846, #59851, #60599, #60289) Thanks @al3mart, @emonty, and @efe-arv.",
      "Android/Talk 模式: 取消 in-flight `talk.speak` playback when speech is explicitly stopped, so stale replies 停止 starting after barge-in or manual 停止. (#61164) Thanks @obviyus.",
      "Android/Talk Mode: restore spoken assistant replies on node-scoped sessions by keeping reply routing synced to the resolved node session key and pausing mic capture during reply playback. (#60306) Thanks @MKV21.",
      "Android/Talk Mode: restore voice replies on gateway-backed talk mode sessions by updating embedded runner transport overrides to the current agent transport API. (#61214) Thanks @obviyus.",
      "Voice-call/OpenAI: pass full 插件 配置 into realtime transcription provider resolution so streaming calls can discover the bundled OpenAI realtime transcription provider again. 修复es #60936. Thanks @sliekens and @vincentkoc.",
      "Control 界面/chat: 添加 a per-session thinking-level picker in the chat header and mobile chat settings, and keep the browser bundle on 界面-local thinking/session-key helpers so Safari no longer crashes on Node-only imports before rendering chat controls.",
      "Control 界面: keep Stop visible during tool-only execution, preserve pending-send busy state, and clear stale ClawHub search results as soon as the query changes. (#54528, #59800, #60267) Thanks @chziyue and @frankekn.",
      "控制 界面/avatar: honor `界面.assistant.avatar` when serving `/avatar/:agentId` so Appearance 界面 avatar paths 停止 falling 返回 to initials placeholders. (#60778) Thanks @hannasdev.",
      "Control 界面/cron: highlight the Cron refresh button while refresh is in flight so the page's loading state stays visible even when prior data remains on screen. (#60394) Thanks @coder-zhuzm.",
      "控制 界面/Overview: 防止 gateway 访问 token/password visibility 切换器 buttons from overlapping their inputs at narrow widths. (#56924) Thanks @bbddbb1.",
      "CLI/skills JSON: route `skills 列表 --json`, `skills 信息 --json`, and `skills check --json` 输出 to stdout instead of stderr so machine-readable consumers receive JSON on the expected stream again. (#60914; 修复es #57599; landed from contributor PR #57611 by @Aftabbs) Thanks @Aftabbs.",
      "CLI/Commander: preserve Commander-computed 退出 codes for argument and help-错误 paths, and cover the 用户-argv parse 模式 in the regression tests so 无效 CLI invocations no longer 报告 成功 when exits are intercepted. (#60923) Thanks @Linux2010.",
      "Cron: replay interrupted recurring jobs on the 第一个 gateway restart instead of 等待中 for a second restart. (#60583) Thanks @joelnishanth.",
      "Cron: send failure notifications through the job's primary delivery channel using the same 会话 上下文 as successful delivery when no explicit `failureDestination` is configured. (#60622) Thanks @artwalker.",
      "Live model switching: only treat explicit 用户-driven model changes as 待处理 live switches, so fallback rotation, heartbeat overrides, and compaction no longer trip `LiveSessionModelSwitchError` before making an API call. (#60266) Thanks @kiranvk-2011.",
      "Exec approvals: reuse durable exact-command `允许-always` approvals in allowlist 模式 so identical reruns 停止 prompting, and tighten Windows interpreter/路径 approval handling so wrapper and malformed-路径 cases fail closed more consistently. (#59880, #59780, #58040, #59182) Thanks @luoyanglang, @SnowSky1, and @pgondhi987.",
      "Node exec approvals: keep node-host `系统.运行` approvals bound to the prepared execution plan across async forwarding, so mutable script operands still get approval-time binding and drift revalidation instead of dropping 返回 to unbound execution.",
      "Agents/exec approvals: let `exec-approvals.json` agent 安全 覆盖 stricter gateway 工具 defaults so approved subagents can use `安全: “full”` without falling 返回 to allowlist enforcement again. (#60310) Thanks @lml2468.",
      "Agents/exec: restore `host=node` routing for node-pinned and `host=auto` sessions, while still blocking sandboxed `auto` sessions from jumping to gateway. (#60788) Thanks @openperf.",
      "Exec/heartbeat: use the canonical `exec-event` wake reason for `notifyOnExit` so 背景 exec completions still trigger 关注-向上 turns when `HEARTBEAT.md` is 空 or comments-only. (#41479) Thanks @rstar327.",
      "Heartbeat: skip wake delivery when the target session lane is already busy so the pending event is retried instead of getting drained too early. (#40526) Thanks @lucky7323.",
      "Group chats/agent prompts: tell models to 最小化 空 lines and use normal chat-style 间距 so group replies avoid document-style blank-line formatting.",
      "Providers/OpenAI GPT: treat short approval turns 点赞 `ok do it` and `go ahead` as immediate action turns, and trim overly memo-点赞 GPT-5 chat confirmations so OpenAI replies stay shorter and more conversational by default.",
      "Providers/OpenAI Codex: 拆分 native `contextWindow` from runtime `contextTokens`, keep the default effective cap at `272000`, and expose a per-model `contextTokens` 覆盖 on `models.providers.*.models[]`.",
      "Providers/OpenAI-compatible WS: compute fallback token totals from normalized usage when providers omit or zero `total_tokens`, so DashScope-compatible sessions 停止 storing zero totals after alias normalization. (#54940) Thanks @lyfuci.",
      "Agents/OpenAI: mark Claude-compatible 文件 工具 schemas as `添加itionalProperties: false` so direct OpenAI GPT-5 routes 停止 rejecting the `read` 工具 with 无效 strict-schema errors.",
      "Agents/OpenAI: fall 返回 to `strict: false` for native OpenAI 工具 calls when a 工具 schema is not strict-compatible, and normalize 空-object 工具 schemas to include `req界面red: []`, so direct GPT-5 routes 停止 failing with 无效 strict-schema errors 点赞 missing `路径` in `req界面red`.",
      "Agents/GPT: 添加 explicit work-item lifecycle events for embedded runs, use them to surface real progress more reliably, and stop counting tool-started turns as planning-only retries.",
      "插件s/OpenAI: 启用 `gpt-镜像-1` reference-镜像 edits through `/images/edits` multipart uploads, and 停止 inferring un支持ed resolution overrides when no explicit `大小` or `resolution` is provided.",
      "Agents/replay: 移除 the malformed assistant-content canonicalization repair from replay history sanitization instead of extending that legacy repair 路径 into replay validation.",
      "插件s/OpenAI: tune the OpenAI prompt overlay for live-chat cadence so GPT replies stay shorter, more human, and less wall-of-text by default.",
      "Providers/compat: 停止 forcing OpenAI-only defaults on proxy and custom OpenAI-compatible routes, preserve native vendor-specific reasoning/工具/streaming behavior across Anthropic-compatible, Moonshot, Mistral, ModelStudio, OpenRouter, xAI, and Z.ai endpoints, and route GitHub Copilot Claude models through Anthropic Messages instead of OpenAI Responses.",
      "Providers/GitHub Copilot: send IDE identity headers on runtime model requests and GitHub token exchange so IDE-authenticated Copilot runs 停止 failing with missing `Editor-版本`. (#60641) Thanks @VACInc and @vincentkoc.",
      "Providers/OpenRouter failover: classify `403 “Key limit exceeded”` spending-limit responses as billing so model fallback continues instead of stopping on generic 认证. (#59892) Thanks @rockcent.",
      "Providers/Anthropic: keep `claude-cli/*` 认证 on live Claude CLI credentials at runtime, avoid persisting stale bearer-token profiles, and suppress macOS Keychain prompts during non-interactive Claude CLI setup. (#61234) Thanks @darkamenosa.",
      "Providers/Anthropic: when Claude CLI 认证 becomes the default, write a real `claude-cli` 认证 profile so local and gateway agent runs can use Claude CLI immediately without missing-API-key failures. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Providers/Anthropic Vertex: honor `cacheRetention: “long”` with the real 1-hour prompt-cache TTL on Vertex AI endpoints, and default `anthropic-vertex` cache retention 点赞 direct Anthropic. (#60888) Thanks @affsantos.",
      "Agents/Anthropic: preserve native `toolu_*` replay ids on direct Anthropic and Anthropic Vertex paths so cache-sensitive history stops rewriting known-valid Anthropic tool-use ids. (#52612)",
      "Providers/Google: 添加 model-level `cacheRetention` 支持 for direct Gemini 系统 prompts by creating, reusing, and refreshing `cachedContents` automatically on Google AI Studio runs. (#51372) Thanks @rafaelmariano-glitch.",
      "Google Gemini CLI auth: detect bundled npm installs by scanning packaged bundle files for the Gemini OAuth client config, so `npm install -g @google/gemini-cli` layouts work again. (#60486) Thanks @wzfmini01.",
      "Google Gemini CLI 认证: detect personal OAuth 模式 from local Gemini settings and 跳过 Code Assist project discovery for those logins, so personal Google accounts 停止 failing with `loadCodeAssist 400 Bad Request`. (#49226) Thanks @bobworrall.",
      "Google Gemini CLI 认证: 改进 OAuth credential discovery across Windows nvm and Homebrew libexec installs, and 对齐 Code Assist metadata so Gemini 登录 stops failing on packaged CLI layouts. (#40729) Thanks @hughcube.",
      "Google Gemini CLI models: 添加 前进-compat 支持 for 稳定 `gemini-2.5-*` model ids by letting the bundled CLI provider clone them from Google templates, so `gemini-2.5-flash-lite` and related configured models 停止 showing 向上 as missing. (#35274) Thanks @mySebbe.",
      "Google 镜像 generation: 禁用 pinned DNS for Gemini 镜像 requests and honor explicit `pinDns` overrides in shared provider HTTP helpers so proxy-backed 镜像 generation works again. (#59873) Thanks @luoyanglang.",
      "Providers/Microsoft Foundry: preserve explicit 镜像 capability on normalized Foundry deployments, repair stale GPT/o-series text-only model metadata across gateway and runtime paths, and keep unknown fallback models from borrowing unrelated 镜像 支持.",
      "Providers/Model Studio: preserve native streaming usage reporting for DashScope-compatible endpoints even when they are configured under a generic provider key, so streamed token totals 停止 sticking at zero. (#52395) Thanks @IVY-AI-gif.",
      "Providers/Z.AI: preserve explicitly registered `glm-5-*` variants 点赞 `glm-5-turbo` instead of intercepting them with the generic GLM-5 前进-compat shim. (#48185) Thanks @haoyu-haoyu.",
      "Amazon Bedrock/aws-sdk auth: stop injecting the fake `AWS_PROFILE` APIKey marker when no AWS auth env vars exist, so instance-role and other default-chain setups keep working without poisoning provider config. (#61194) Thanks @wirjo.",
      "Agents/Kimi 工具-call repair: preserve 工具 arguments that were already present on streamed 工具 calls when later malformed deltas fail reevaluation, while still dropping stale repair-only state before `toolcall_end`.",
      "插件s/Kimi Coding: parse tagged tool calls and keep Anthropic-native tool payloads so Kimi coding endpoints execute tools instead of echoing raw markup. (#60051, #60391) Thanks @obviyus and @Eric-Guo.",
      "Media understanding: auto-注册 镜像-capable 配置 providers for vision routing, so custom GLM-style provider ids with 镜像 models 停止 failing with “no media-understanding provider registered”. (#51418) Thanks @xydt-610.",
      "插件s/media understanding: 启用 bundled Groq and Deepgram providers by default so configured transcription models work without extra 插件 activation 配置. (#59982) Thanks @yxjsxy.",
      "MiniMax/pricing: keep bundled MiniMax highspeed pricing distinct in provider catalogs and preserve the lower M2.5 cache-read pricing when onboarding older MiniMax models. (#54214) Thanks @octo-patch.",
      "MiniMax: advertise 镜像 输入框 on bundled `MiniMax-M2.7` and `MiniMax-M2.7-highspeed` model definitions so 镜像-capable flows can route through the M2.7 family correctly. (#54843) Thanks @MerlinMiao88888888.",
      "Models/MiniMax: honor `MINIMAX_API_HOST` for implicit bundled MiniMax provider catalogs so China-hosted API-key setups pick `API.minimaxi.com/anthropic` without manual provider 配置. (#34524) Thanks @caiqinghua.",
      "Usage/MiniMax: invert remaining-style `usage_percent` fields when MiniMax reports only remaining percentage 数据, so usage bars 停止 showing nearly-full remaining quota as nearly-exhausted usage. (#60254) Thanks @jwchmodx.",
      "Usage/MiniMax: let usage snapshots treat `minimax-portal` and MiniMax CN aliases as the same MiniMax quota surface, and prefer stored MiniMax OAuth before falling back to Coding Plan keys.",
      "Usage/MiniMax: prefer the chat-model `model_remains` entry and derive Coding Plan window labels from MiniMax interval timestamps so MiniMax usage snapshots 停止 picking zero-budget media rows and misreporting 4h windows as `5h`. (#52349) Thanks @IVY-AI-gif.",
      "Model picker/providers: treat bundled BytePlus and Volcengine plan aliases as their native providers during setup, and expose their bundled standard/coding catalogs before 认证 so setup can suggest the 向右 models. (#58819) Thanks @Luckymingxuan.",
      "Tools/web_search (Kimi): when `tools.web.搜索.kimi.baseUrl` is unset, inherit native Moonshot chat `baseUrl` (`.ai` / `.cn`) so China console keys authenticate on the same host as chat. 修复es #44851. (#56769) Thanks @tonga54.",
      "Agents/Claude CLI: keep non-interactive `--权限-模式 bypassPermissions` when custom `cliBackends.claude-cli.args` 覆盖 defaults, including fallback resolution before the runtime 插件 registry is 激活, so cron and heartbeat Claude CLI runs do not regress to interactive approval 模式. (#61114) Thanks @cathrynlavery and @thewilloftheshadow.",
      "Agents/Claude CLI: persist explicit `openclaw agent --会话-id` runs under a 稳定 会话 key so 关注-ups can reuse the stored CLI binding and 恢复 the same underlying Claude 会话.",
      "Agents/Claude CLI: persist routed Claude 会话 bindings, 旋转 them on `/新增` and `/重置`, and keep live Claude CLI model switches moving across the configured Claude family so resumed sessions 关注 the real 激活 thread and model. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Agents/CLI backends: invalidate stored CLI 会话 reuse when local CLI 登录 state or the 选中 认证 profile credential changes, so relogin and token rotation 停止 resuming stale sessions.",
      "Agents/Claude CLI/images: reuse 稳定 hydrated 镜像 文件 paths and preserve shared media extensions 点赞 HEIC when passing 镜像 refs to local CLI runs, so Claude CLI 镜像 prompts 停止 thrashing KV cache pre修复es and oddball 镜像 formats do not fall 返回 to `.bin`. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Agents/compaction: keep assistant 工具 calls and displaced 工具 results in the same compaction chunk so strict summarization providers 停止 rejecting orphaned 工具 pairs. (#58849) Thanks @openperf.",
      "Agents/failover: scope Anthropic `An unknown error occurred` failover matching by provider so generic internal unknown-error text no longer triggers retryable timeout fallback. (#59325) Thanks @aaron-he-zhu.",
      "Agents/subagents: honor allowlist validation, 认证-profile handoff, and 会话 覆盖 state when a subagent retries after `LiveSessionModelSwitchError`. (#58178) Thanks @openperf.",
      "Agents/runtime: make default subagent allowlists, inherited skills/workspaces, and duplicate 会话-id resolution behave more predictably, and include 值-shape hints in missing-参数 工具 errors. (#59944, #59992, #59858, #55317) Thanks @hclsys, @gumadeiras, @joelnishanth, and @priyansh19.",
      "Agents/pairing: 合并 completion announce delivery 上下文 with the requester 会话 fallback so missing `to` still reaches the original channel, and include `operator.talk.secrets` in CLI default operator scopes for node-role device pairing approvals. (#56481) Thanks @maxpetrusenko.",
      "Agents/scheduling: steer 背景-now work toward automatic completion wake and treat `process` polling as on-demand inspection or intervention instead of default completion handling. (#60877) Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Agents/skills: 跳过 `.git` and `node_modules` when mirroring skills into 沙箱 workspaces so read-only sandboxes do not copy repo history or dependency trees. (#61090) Thanks @joelnishanth.",
      "ACP/agents: inherit the target agent workspace for cross-agent ACP spawns and fall back safely when the inherited workspace no longer exists. (#58438) Thanks @zssggle-rgb.",
      "ACPX/Windows: preserve backslashes and absolute `.exe` paths in Claude CLI parsing, and fail fast on wrapper-script targets with g界面dance to use `cmd.exe /c`, `powershell.exe -文件`, or `node <script>`. (#60689) Thanks @steipete.",
      "认证/failover: persist 选中 fallback overrides before retrying, shorten `auth_permanent` lockouts, and 刷新 websocket/shared-认证 sessions only when real 认证 changes occur so retries and secret rotations behave predictably. (#60404, #60323, #60387) Thanks @extrasmall0 and @mappel-nv.",
      "Gateway/channels: 置顶 the 初始 startup channel registry before later 插件-registry churn so configured channels stay 可见 and `channels.状态` stops falling 返回 to 空 `channelOrder` / `channels` payloads after runtime 插件 loads.",
      "Prompt caching: order 稳定 workspace project-上下文 files before `HEARTBEAT.md` and keep `HEARTBEAT.md` below the 系统-prompt cache boundary so heartbeat churn does not invalidate the 稳定 project-上下文 pre修复. (#58979) Thanks @yozu and @vincentkoc.",
      "Prompt caching: route Codex Responses and Anthropic Vertex through boundary-aware cache shAPIng, and 报告 the actual outbound 系统 prompt in cache traces so cache reuse and misses line 向上 with what providers really receive. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Agents/cache: preserve the full 3-turn prompt-cache 镜像 window across 工具 loops, keep colliding bundled MCP 工具 definitions deterministic, and reapply Anthropic Vertex cache shAPIng after payload hook replacements so KV/cache reuse stays 稳定. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "状态/cache: 恢复 `cacheRead` and `cacheWrite` in transcript fallback so `/状态` keeps showing cache hit percentages when 会话 logs are the only 完成 usage source. (#59247) Thanks @stuartsy.",
      "状态/usage: let `/状态` and `session_status` fall 返回 to transcript token totals when the 会话 meta store stayed at zero, so LM Studio, Ollama, DashScope, and similar OpenAI-compatible providers 停止 showing `上下文: 0/...`. (#55041) Thanks @jjjojoj.",
      "Mattermost/配置 schema: accept `groups.*.req界面reMention` again so existing Mattermost configs no longer fail strict validation after upgrade. (#58271) Thanks @MoerAI.",
      "Doctor/配置: compare normalized `talk` configs by deep structural equality instead of key-order-sensitive serialization so `openclaw doctor --修复` stops repeatedly reporting/applying no-op `talk.provider/providers` normalization. (#59911) Thanks @ejames-开发.",
      "Anthropic CLI onboarding: rewrite migrated fallback model refs during non-interactive Claude CLI setup too, so onboarding and scripted setup no longer keep stale `anthropic/*` fallbacks after switching the primary model to `claude-cli/*`. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Models/Anthropic CLI 认证: 替换 migrated `agents.defaults.models` allowlists when `openclaw models 认证 登录 --provider anthropic --method cli --set-default` switches to `claude-cli/*`, so stale `anthropic/*` entries do not linger beside the migrated Claude CLI defaults. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Doctor/Claude CLI: 添加 dedicated Claude CLI health checks so `openclaw doctor` can spot missing local installs or broken 认证 before agent runs fail. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "插件s/认证-choice: apply provider-owned 认证 配置 patches without recursively preserving replaced default-model maps, so Anthropic Claude CLI and similar migrations can intentionally swap model allowlists during onboarding and setup instead of accumulating stale entries. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "插件s/onboarding: write dotted 插件 界面Hint paths 点赞 Brave `webSearch.模式` as nested 插件 配置 so `llm-上下文` setup stops failing validation. (#61159) Thanks @obviyus.",
      "插件s/安装: preserve unsafe 覆盖 flags across linked 插件 and hook-pack probes so local `--链接` installs honor the documented 覆盖 behavior. (#60624) Thanks @JerrettDavis.",
      "插件s/cache: inherit the 激活 gateway workspace for provider, web-搜索, and web-fetch snapshot loads when callers omit `workspaceDir`, so compatible 插件 registries and snapshot caches 停止 missing on gateway-owned runtime paths. (#61138) Thanks @jzakirov.",
      "插件 SDK/上下文 engines: export the missing 上下文-engine result and subagent lifecycle types from `openclaw/插件-sdk` so 上下文 engine 插件s can 类型 `ContextEngine` 实现ations without local workarounds. (#61251) Thanks @DaevMithran.",
      "Tasks/maintenance: reconcile stale cron and chat-backed CLI task rows against live cron-job and agent-运行 ownership instead of treating any persisted 会话 key as proof that the task is still running. (#60310) Thanks @lml2468.",
      "插件s: suppress trust-警告 noise during non-activating snapshot and CLI metadata loads. (#61427) Thanks @gumadeiras.",
      "Agents/video generation: accept `agents.defaults.videoGenerationModel` in strict 配置 validation and `openclaw 配置 set/get`, so gateways using `video_generate` no longer fail to boot after enabling a video model.",
      "Matrix/streaming: 添加 a q界面et 预览 模式 for streamed Matrix replies, keep legacy `partial` 预览-第一个 behavior, and finalize q界面et media captions correctly so previews 停止 notifying early without dropping 最终 text semantics. (#61450) Thanks @gumadeiras.",
      "Gateway/shutdown: bound websocket-server shutdown even when no tracked clients remain, so gateway restarts stop hanging until the watchdog kills the process. (#61565) Thanks @mbelinky.",
      "控制 界面/multilingual: localize the remaining shared channel, instances, nodes, and gateway-confirmation strings so the dashboard stops mixing translated 界面 with hardcoded English labels. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Discord/media: raise the default inbound and outbound media cap to `100MB` so Discord matches Telegram more closely and larger attachments 停止 failing on the old low default.",
      "Matrix: keep direct transport requests on the pinned dispatcher by routing them through undici runtime fetch, so Matrix clients 恢复 syncing on newer runtimes without dropping the validated 添加ress binding. (#61595) Thanks @gumadeiras.",
      "插件s/facades: resolve globally installed bundled-插件 runtime facades from registry roots so bundled channels 点赞 LINE still boot when the winning 插件 安装 lives under the global extensions 目录 with an encoded scoped 文件夹 name. (#61297) Thanks @openperf."
    ]
  }
},
  {
  "version": "2026.4.2",
  "date": "2026-04-02",
  "type": "稳定版",
  "latest": false,
  "changes": {
    "features": [
      "Tasks/Task Flow: 恢复 the core Task Flow substrate with managed-vs-mirrored sync modes, durable flow state/revision tracking, and `openclaw flows` inspection/恢复 primitives so 背景 orchestration can persist and be operated separately from 插件 authoring layers. (#58930) Thanks @mbelinky.",
      "Tasks/Task Flow: 添加 managed child task spawning plus sticky 取消 intent, so external orchestrators can 停止 scheduling immediately and let parent Task Flows settle to `cancelled` once 激活 child tasks finish. (#59610) Thanks @mbelinky.",
      "插件s/Task Flow: 添加 a bound `API.runtime.taskFlow` seam so 插件s and trusted authoring layers can 创建 and drive managed Task Flows from host-resolved OpenClaw 上下文 without passing owner identifiers on each call. (#59622) Thanks @mbelinky.",
      "Android/assistant: 添加 assistant-role entrypoints plus Google Assistant 应用 Actions metadata so Android can launch OpenClaw from the assistant trigger and hand prompts into the chat composer. (#59596) Thanks @obviyus.",
      "Exec defaults: make gateway/node host exec default to YOLO 模式 by requesting `安全=full` with `ask=off`, and 对齐 host approval-文件 fallbacks plus docs/doctor reporting with that no-prompt default.",
      "Providers/runtime: 添加 provider-owned replay hook surfaces for transcript policy, replay cleanup, and reasoning-模式 dispatch. (#59143) Thanks @jalehman.",
      "插件s/hooks: 添加 `before_agent_reply` so 插件s can short-circ界面t the LLM with synthetic replies after inline actions. (#20067) Thanks @JoshuaLelon.",
      "Channels/会话 routing: move provider-specific 会话 conversation grammar into 插件-owned 会话-key surfaces, preserving Telegram topic routing and Feishu scoped inheritance across bootstrap, model 覆盖, restart, and 工具-policy paths.",
      "Feishu/comments: 添加 a dedicated Drive comment-event flow with comment-thread 上下文 resolution, in-thread replies, and `feishu_drive` comment actions for document collaboration workflows. (#58497) Thanks @wittam-01.",
      "Matrix/插件: emit spec-compliant `m.mentions` metadata across text sends, media captions, edits, poll fallback text, and action-driven edits so Matrix mentions notify reliably in clients 点赞 Element. (#59323) Thanks @gumadeiras.",
      "Diffs: 添加 插件-owned `viewerBaseUrl` so viewer links can use a 稳定 proxy/public origin without passing `baseUrl` on every 工具 call. (#59341) Related #59227. Thanks @gumadeiras.",
      "Agents/compaction: resolve `agents.defaults.compaction.model` consistently for manual `/compact` and other 上下文-engine compaction paths, so engine-owned compaction uses the configured 覆盖 model across runtime entrypoints. (#56710) Thanks @oliviareid-svg.",
      "Agents/compaction: 添加 `agents.defaults.compaction.notifyUser` so the `🧹 Compacting 上下文...` 开始 notice is opt-in instead of always being shown. (#54251) Thanks @oguricap0327.",
      "WhatsApp/reactions: 添加 `reactionLevel` g界面dance for agent reactions. Thanks @mcaxtr.",
      "Exec approvals/channels: auto-启用 DM-第一个 native chat approvals when 支持ed channels can infer approvers from existing owner 配置, while keeping channel fanout explicit and clarifying forwarding versus native approval 客户端 配置."
    ],
    "improvements": [
      "插件s/xAI: move `x_search` settings from the legacy core `tools.web.x_search.*` 路径 to the 插件-owned `插件s.entries.xai.配置.xSearch.*` 路径, standardize `x_search` 认证 on `插件s.entries.xai.配置.webSearch.APIKey` / `XAI_API_KEY`, and migrate legacy 配置 with `openclaw doctor --修复`. (#59674) Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "插件s/web fetch: move Firecrawl `web_fetch` 配置 from the legacy core `tools.web.fetch.firecrawl.*` 路径 to the 插件-owned `插件s.entries.firecrawl.配置.webFetch.*` 路径, route `web_fetch` fallback through the 新增 fetch-provider boundary instead of a Firecrawl-only core branch, and migrate legacy 配置 with `openclaw doctor --修复`. (#59465) Thanks @vincentkoc."
    ],
    "bugfixes": [
      "Providers/transport policy: centralize request 认证, proxy, TLS, and header shAPIng across shared HTTP, stream, and websocket paths, block insecure TLS/runtime transport overrides, and keep proxy-hop TLS separate from target mTLS settings. (#59682) Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Providers/Copilot: classify native GitHub Copilot API hosts in the shared provider endpoint resolver and harden token-derived proxy endpoint parsing so Copilot base 链接 routing stays centralized and fails closed on malformed hints. (#59644) Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Providers/streaming headers: centralize default and attribution header merging across OpenAI websocket, embedded-runner, and proxy stream paths so provider-specific headers stay consistent and caller overrides only win where intended. (#59542) Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Providers/media HTTP: centralize base 链接 normalization, default 认证/header injection, and explicit header 覆盖 handling across shared OpenAI-compatible audio, Deepgram audio, Gemini media/镜像, and Moonshot video request paths. (#59469) Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Providers/OpenAI-compatible routing: centralize native-vs-proxy request policy so 隐藏 attribution and related OpenAI-family defaults only apply on verified native endpoints across stream, websocket, and shared audio HTTP paths. (#59433) Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Providers/Anthropic routing: centralize native-vs-proxy endpoint classification for direct Anthropic `service_tier` handling so spoofed or proxied hosts do not inherit native Anthropic defaults. (#59608) Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Gateway/exec loopback: restore legacy-role fallback for empty paired-device token maps and allow silent local role upgrades so local exec and node clients stop failing with pairing-req界面red errors after `2026.3.31`. (#59092) Thanks @openperf.",
      "Agents/subagents: pin admin-only subagent gateway calls to `operator.admin` while keeping `agent` at least privilege, so `sessions_spawn` no longer dies on loopback scope-upgrade pairing with `close(1008) \"pairing req界面red\"`. (#59555) Thanks @openperf.",
      "Exec approvals/配置: strip 无效 `安全`, `ask`, and `askFallback` values from `~/.openclaw/exec-approvals.json` during normalization so malformed policy enums fall 返回 cleanly to the documented defaults instead of corrupting runtime policy resolution. (#59112) Thanks @openperf.",
      "Exec approvals/doctor: 报告 host policy sources from the real approvals 文件 路径 and 忽略 malformed host 覆盖 values when attributing effective policy conflicts. (#59367) Thanks @gumadeiras.",
      "Exec/runtime: treat `tools.exec.host=auto` as routing-only, keep implicit no-配置 exec on 沙箱 when available or gateway otherwise, and reject per-call host overrides that would 绕过 the configured 沙箱 or host target. (#58897) Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Slack/mrkdwn formatting: 添加 b界面lt-in Slack mrkdwn g界面dance in inbound 上下文 so Slack replies 停止 falling 返回 to generic Markdown patterns that render poorly in Slack. (#59100) Thanks @jadewon.",
      "WhatsApp/presence: send `unavailable` presence on 连接 in self-chat 模式 so personal-手机 users 停止 losing all 推送 notifications while the gateway is running. (#59410) Thanks @mcaxtr.",
      "WhatsApp/media: 添加 HTML, XML, and CSS to the MIME map and fall 返回 gracefully for unknown media types instead of dropping the attachment. (#51562) Thanks @bobbyt74.",
      "Matrix/onboarding: 恢复 g界面ded setup in `openclaw channels 添加` and `openclaw configure --section channels`, while keeping custom 插件 wizards on the shared `setupWizard` seam. (#59462) Thanks @gumadeiras.",
      "Matrix/streaming: keep live partial previews for the current assistant block while preserving completed block 更新s as separate messages when `channels.matrix.blockStreaming` is enabled. (#59384) Thanks @gumadeiras.",
      "Feishu/comment threads: harden document comment-thread delivery so whole-document comments fall back to `添加_comment`, delayed reply lookups retry more reliably, and user-visible replies avoid reasoning/planning spillover. (#59129) Thanks @wittam-01.",
      "MS Teams/streaming: strip already-streamed text from fallback block delivery when replies exceed the 4000-character streaming limit so long responses 停止 duplicating content. (#59297) Thanks @bradgroux.",
      "Slack/thread 上下文: 筛选 thread starter and history by the effective conversation allowlist without dropping 有效 打开-room, DM, or group DM 上下文. (#58380) Thanks @jacobtomlinson.",
      "Mattermost/probes: route 状态 probes through the SSRF guard and honor `allowPrivateNetwork` so connectivity checks stay safe for self-hosted Mattermost deployments. (#58529) Thanks @mappel-nv.",
      "Zalo/webhook replay: scope replay dedupe key by chat and sender so reused message IDs across different chats or senders no longer collide, and harden metadata reads for partially missing payloads. (#58444)",
      "QQBot/structured payloads: restrict local 文件 paths to QQ Bot-owned media storage, block traversal outside that root, reduce 路径 leakage in logs, and keep inline 镜像 数据 URLs working. (#58453) Thanks @jacobtomlinson.",
      "镜像 generation/providers: route OpenAI, MiniMax, and fal 镜像 requests through the shared provider HTTP transport 路径 so custom base URLs, guarded private-网络 routing, and provider request defaults stay aligned with the rest of provider HTTP. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "镜像 generation/providers: 停止 inferring private-网络 访问 from configured OpenAI, MiniMax, and fal 镜像 base URLs, and cap shared HTTP 错误-body reads so hostile or misconfigured endpoints fail closed without relaxing SSRF policy or buffering unbounded 错误 payloads. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Browser/host inspection: keep static Chrome inspection helpers out of the activated browser runtime so `openclaw doctor browser` and related checks do not eagerly 加载 the bundled browser 插件. (#59471) Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Browser/CDP: normalize trailing-dot localhost absolute-表单 hosts before loopback checks so remote CDP websocket URLs 点赞 `ws://localhost.:...` rewrite 返回 to the configured remote host. (#59236) Thanks @mappel-nv.",
      "Agents/输出 sanitization: strip namespaced `antml:thinking` blocks from 用户-可见 text so Anthropic-style internal monologue tags do not leak into replies. (#59550) Thanks @obviyus.",
      "Kimi Coding/tools: normalize Anthropic 工具 payloads into the OpenAI-compatible function shape Kimi Coding expects so 工具 calls 停止 losing req界面red arguments. (#59440) Thanks @obviyus.",
      "镜像 工具/paths: resolve relative local media paths against the agent `workspaceDir` instead of `process.cwd()` so inputs 点赞 `inbox/receipt.png` pass the local-路径 allowlist reliably. (#57222) Thanks Priyansh Gupta.",
      "Podman/launch: 移除 noisy container output from `scripts/run-openclaw-podman.sh` and align the Podman install g界面dance with the q界面eter startup flow. (#59368) Thanks @sallyom.",
      "插件s/runtime: keep LINE reply directives and browser-backed cleanup/重置 flows working even when those 插件s are 禁用 while tightening bundled 插件 activation guards. (#59412) Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "ACP/gateway reconnects: keep ACP prompts alive across transient websocket drops while still failing boundedly when reconnect 恢复 does not 完成. (#59473) Thanks @obviyus.",
      "ACP/gateway reconnects: reject stale pre-ack ACP prompts after reconnect grace expiry so callers fail cleanly instead of hanging indefinitely when the gateway never confirms the 运行.",
      "Gateway/会话 kill: enforce HTTP operator scopes on 会话 kill requests and gate 授权 before 会话 lookup so unauthenticated callers cannot probe 会话 existence. (#59128) Thanks @jacobtomlinson.",
      "MS Teams/logging: format non-`错误` failures with the shared unknown-错误 helper so logs 停止 collapsing caught SDK or Axios objects into `[object Object]`. (#59321) Thanks @bradgroux.",
      "Channels/setup: 忽略 untrusted workspace channel 插件s during setup resolution so a shadowing workspace 插件 cannot 覆盖 b界面lt-in channel setup/登录 flows unless explicitly trusted in 配置. (#59158) Thanks @mappel-nv.",
      "Exec/Windows: 恢复 allowlist enforcement with quote-aware `argPattern` matching across gateway and node exec, and surface accurate dynamic pre-approved executable hints in the exec 工具 description. (#56285) Thanks @kpngr.",
      "Gateway: prune 空 `node-待处理-work` state entries after explicit acknowledgments and natural expiry so the per-node state map no longer grows indefinitely. (#58179) Thanks @gavyngong.",
      "Webhooks/secret comparison: 替换 ad-hoc timing-safe secret comparisons across BlueBubbles, Feishu, Mattermost, Telegram, Twilio, and Zalo webhook handlers with the shared `safeEqualSecret` helper and reject 空 认证 tokens in BlueBubbles. (#58432) Thanks @eleqtrizit.",
      "OpenShell/mirror: constrain `remoteWorkspaceDir` and `remoteAgentWorkspaceDir` to the managed `/沙箱` and `/agent` roots, and keep mirror sync from overwriting or removing 用户-添加ed shell roots during 配置 synchronization. (#58515) Thanks @eleqtrizit.",
      "插件s/activation: preserve explicit, auto-enabled, and default activation provenance plus reason metadata across CLI, gateway bootstrap, and 状态 surfaces so 插件 enablement state stays accurate after auto-启用 resolution. (#59641) Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Exec/env: block 添加itional host 环境 覆盖 pivots for package roots, language runtimes, compiler include paths, and credential/配置 locations so request-scoped exec cannot redirect trusted toolchains or 配置 lookups. (#59233) Thanks @drobison00.",
      "Dotenv/workspace overrides: block workspace `.env` files from overriding `OPENCLAW_PINNED_PYTHON` and `OPENCLAW_PINNED_WRITE_PYTHON` so trusted helper interpreters cannot be redirected by repo-local env injection. (#58473) Thanks @eleqtrizit.",
      "插件s/安装: accept JSON5 syntax in `openclaw.插件.json` and bundle `插件.json` manifests during 安装/validation, so third-party 插件s with trailing commas, comments, or unquoted keys no longer fail to 安装. (#59084) Thanks @singleGanghood.",
      "Telegram/exec approvals: rewrite shared `/approve … 允许-always` callback payloads to `/approve … always` before Telegram 按钮 rendering so 插件 approval IDs still fit Telegram's `callback_data` limit and keep the 允许 Always action 可见. (#59217) Thanks @jameslcowan.",
      "Cron/exec timeouts: surface timed-out `exec` and `bash` failures in isolated cron runs even when `verbose: off`, including custom 会话-target cron jobs, so scheduled runs 停止 failing silently. (#58247) Thanks @skainguyen1412.",
      "Telegram/exec approvals: fall back to the origin session key for async approval followups and keep resume-failure status delivery sanitized so Telegram followups still land without leaking raw exec metadata. (#59351) Thanks @seonang.",
      "Node-host/exec approvals: 绑定 `pnpm dlx` invocations through the approval planner's mutable-script 路径 so the effective runtime command is resolved for approval instead of being 向左 unbound. (#58374)",
      "Exec/node hosts: 停止 forwarding the gateway workspace cwd to remote node exec when no workdir was explicitly requested, so cross-平台 node approvals fall 返回 to the node default cwd instead of failing with `SYSTEM_RUN_DENIED`. (#58977) Thanks @Starhappysh.",
      "Exec approvals/channels: decouple initiating-surface approval availability from native delivery enablement so Telegram, Slack, and Discord still expose approvals when approvers exist and native target routing is configured separately. (#59776) Thanks @joelnishanth."
    ]
  }
},
  {
  "version": "2026.4.1",
  "date": "2026-04-01",
  "type": "稳定版",
  "latest": false,
  "changes": {
    "features": [
      "Tasks/chat: 添加 `/tasks` as a chat-native 背景 task board for the current 会话, with recent task details and agent-local fallback counts when no linked tasks are 可见. Related #54226. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Web 搜索/SearXNG: 添加 the bundled SearXNG provider 插件 for `web_search` with configurable host 支持. (#57317) Thanks @cgdusek.",
      "Amazon Bedrock/Guardrails: 添加 Bedrock Guardrails 支持 to the bundled provider. (#58588) Thanks @MikeORed.",
      "macOS/Voice Wake: 添加 the Voice Wake 选项 to trigger Talk 模式. (#58490) Thanks @SmoothExec.",
      "Feishu/comments: 添加 a dedicated Drive comment-event flow with comment-thread 上下文 resolution, in-thread replies, and `feishu_drive` comment actions for document collaboration workflows. (#58497) Thanks @wittam-01.",
      "Gateway/webchat: make `chat.history` text truncation configurable with `gateway.webchat.chatHistoryMaxChars` and per-request `maxChars`, while preserving silent-reply filtering and existing default payload limits. (#58900)",
      "Agents/default params: 添加 `agents.defaults.params` for global default provider parameters. (#58548) Thanks @lpender.",
      "Agents/failover: cap prompt-side and assistant-side same-provider 认证-profile retries for rate-limit failures before cross-provider model fallback, 添加 the `认证.cooldowns.rateLimitedProfileRotations` knob, and document the 新增 fallback behavior. (#58707) Thanks @Forgely3D",
      "Cron/tools allowlist: 添加 `openclaw cron --tools` for per-job 工具 allowlists. (#58504) Thanks @andyk-ms.",
      "Channels/会话 routing: move provider-specific 会话 conversation grammar into 插件-owned 会话-key surfaces, preserving Telegram topic routing and Feishu scoped inheritance across bootstrap, model 覆盖, restart, and 工具-policy paths.",
      "WhatsApp/reactions: 添加 `reactionLevel` g界面dance for agent reactions. Thanks @mcaxtr.",
      "Telegram/errors: 添加 configurable `errorPolicy` and `errorCooldownMs` controls so Telegram can suppress repeated delivery errors per 账户, chat, and topic without muting distinct failures. (#51914) Thanks @chinar-amrutkar",
      "ZAI/models: 添加 `glm-5.1` and `glm-5v-turbo` to the bundled Z.AI provider catalog. (#58793) Thanks @tomsun28",
      "Agents/compaction: resolve `agents.defaults.compaction.model` consistently for manual `/compact` and other 上下文-engine compaction paths, so engine-owned compaction uses the configured 覆盖 model across runtime entrypoints. (#56710) Thanks @oliviareid-svg"
    ],
    "improvements": [],
    "bugfixes": [
      "Chat/错误 replies: 停止 leaking raw provider/runtime failures into external chat channels, return a friendly retry 消息 instead, and 添加 a specific `/新增` hint for Bedrock toolResult/toolUse 会话 mismatches. (#58831) Thanks @ImLukeF.",
      "Gateway/reload: ignore startup config writes by persisted hash in the config reloader so generated auth tokens and seeded Control 界面 origins do not trigger a restart loop, while real `gateway.auth.*` edits still req界面re restart. (#58678) Thanks @yelog",
      "Tasks/gateway: keep the task registry maintenance sweep from stalling the gateway event loop under synchronous SQLite pressure, so upgraded gateways 停止 hanging about a minute after startup. (#58670) Thanks @openperf",
      "Tasks/状态: 隐藏 stale completed 背景 tasks from `/状态` and `session_status`, prefer live task 上下文, and 显示 recent failures only when no 激活 work remains. (#58661) Thanks @vincentkoc",
      "Tasks/gateway: re-check the current task record before maintenance marks runs lost or prunes them, so a task heartbeat or cleanup 更新 that lands during a sweep no longer gets overwritten by stale snapshot state.",
      "Exec/approvals: honor `exec-approvals.json` 安全 defaults when inline or configured 工具 policy is unset, and keep Slack and Discord native approval handling aligned with inferred approvers and real channel enablement so remote exec stops falling into false approval timeouts and 禁用 states. Thanks @scoootscooob and @vincentkoc.",
      "Exec/approvals: make `允许-always` persist as durable 用户-approved trust instead of behaving 点赞 `允许-once`, reuse exact-command trust on shell-wrapper paths that cannot safely persist an executable allowlist entry, keep static allowlist entries from silently bypassing `ask:\"always\"`, and req界面re explicit approval when Windows cannot b界面ld an allowlist execution plan instead of hard-dead-ending remote exec. Thanks @scoootscooob and @vincentkoc.",
      "Exec/cron: resolve isolated cron no-route approval dead-ends from the effective host fallback policy when trusted automation is allowed, and make `openclaw doctor` warn when `tools.exec` is broader than `~/.openclaw/exec-approvals.json` so stricter host-policy conflicts are explicit. Thanks @scoootscooob and @vincentkoc.",
      "Sessions/model switching: keep `/model` changes queued behind busy runs instead of interrupting the 激活 turn, and retarget queued followups so later work picks 向上 the 新增 model as soon as the current turn finishes.",
      "Gateway/HTTP: skip failing HTTP request stages so one broken facade no longer forces every HTTP endpoint to return 500. (#58746) Thanks @yelog",
      "Gateway/nodes: stop pinning live node commands to the approved node-pair record. Node pairing remains a trust/token flow, while per-node `system.run` policy stays in that node's exec approvals config. 修复es #58824.",
      "WebChat/exec approvals: use native approval 界面 g界面dance in agent 系统 prompts instead of telling agents to paste manual `/approve` commands in webchat sessions. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Web 界面/OpenResponses: preserve rewritten stream snapshots in webchat and keep OpenResponses 最终 streamed text aligned when models rewind earlier 输出. (#58641) Thanks @neeravmakwana",
      "Discord/inbound media: pass Discord attachment and sticker downloads through the shared idle-timeout and worker-中止 路径 so slow or stuck inbound media fetches 停止 hanging 消息 处理中. (#58593) Thanks @aquaright1",
      "Telegram/retries: keep non-idempotent sends on the strict safe-send 路径, retry wrapped pre-连接 failures, and preserve `429` / `retry_after` backoff for safe delivery retries. (#51895) Thanks @chinar-amrutkar",
      "Telegram/exec approvals: route topic-aware exec approval followups through Telegram-owned threading and approval-target parsing, so forum-topic approvals stay in the originating topic instead of falling 返回 to the root chat. (#58783)",
      "Telegram/local Bot API: preserve media MIME types for absolute-路径 downloads so local audio files still trigger transcription and other MIME-based handling. (#54603) Thanks @jzakirov",
      "Channels/WhatsApp: pass inbound message timestamp to model context so the AI can see when WhatsApp messages were sent. (#58590) Thanks @Maninae",
      "Channels/QQ Bot: keep `/bot-logs` export gated behind a truly explicit QQBot allowlist, rejecting wildcard and mixed wildcard entries while preserving the real 框架 command 路径. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Channels/插件s: keep bundled channel 插件s loadable from legacy `channels.<id>` 配置 even under restrictive 插件 allowlists, and make `openclaw doctor` warn only on real 插件 blockers instead of misleading setup g界面dance. (#58873) Thanks @obviyus",
      "插件s/bundled runtimes: 恢复 externalized bundled 插件 runtime dependency 预发布 across packed installs, Docker b界面lds, and local runtime 预发布 so bundled 插件s keep their declared runtime deps after the 2026.3.31 externalization 更改. (#58782)",
      "LINE/runtime: resolve the packaged runtime contract from the b界面lt `dist/插件s/runtime` 布局 so LINE channels 开始 correctly again after global npm installs on `2026.3.31`. (#58799) Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "MiniMax/插件s: auto-启用 the bundled MiniMax 插件 for API-key 认证/配置 so MiniMax 镜像 generation and other 插件-owned capabilities 加载 without manual 插件 allowlisting. (#57127) Thanks @tars90percent.",
      "Ollama/model picker: 显示 only Ollama models after provider selection in the CLI picker. (#55290) Thanks @Luckymingxuan.",
      "CDP/profiles: prefer `cdpPort` over stale WebSocket URLs so browser automation reconnects cleanly. (#58499) Thanks @Mlightsnow.",
      "Media/paths: resolve relative `MEDIA` paths against the agent workspace so local attachment references keep working. (#58624) Thanks @aquaright1.",
      "Memory/会话 indexing: keep full reindexes from skipping 会话 transcripts when sync is triggered by `会话-开始` or `watch`, so restart-driven reindexes preserve 会话 memory. (#39732) Thanks @upupc",
      "Memory/QMD: prefer `--mask` over `--glob` when creating QMD collections so default memory collections keep their intended patterns and 停止 colliding on restart. (#58643) Thanks @GitZhangChi.",
      "Subagents/tasks: keep subagent completion and cleanup from crashing when task-registry writes fail, so a corrupt or missing task 行 no longer takes 向下 the gateway during lifecycle finalization. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "沙箱/browser: compare browser runtime inspection against `agents.defaults.沙箱.browser.镜像` so `openclaw 沙箱 列表 --browser` stops reporting healthy browser containers as 镜像 mismatches. (#58759) Thanks @sandpile.",
      "插件s/安装: 前进 `--dangerously-force-unsafe-安装` through 归档 and npm-spec 插件 installs so the documented 覆盖 reaches the 安全 scanner on those 安装 paths. (#58879) Thanks @ryanlee-gemini.",
      "Auto-reply/commands: strip inbound metadata before slash command detection so wrapped `/model`, `/新增`, and `/状态` commands are recognized. (#58725) Thanks @Mlightsnow.",
      "Agents/Anthropic: preserve thinking blocks and signatures across replay, cache-控制 patching, and 上下文 pruning so compacted Anthropic sessions 继续 working instead of failing on later turns. (#58916) Thanks @obviyus",
      "Agents/failover: unify structured and raw provider 错误 classification so provider-specific `400`/`422` payloads no longer get forced into generic format failures before retry, billing, or compaction logic can inspect them. (#58856) Thanks @aaron-he-zhu.",
      "Auth profiles/store: coerce misplaced SecretRef objects out of plaintext `key` and `token` fields during store load so agents without ACP runtime stop crashing on `.trim()` after upgrade. (#58923) Thanks @openperf.",
      "ACPX/runtime: repair `queue owner unavailable` 会话 恢复 by replacing dead named sessions and resuming the backend 会话 when ACPX exposes a 稳定 会话 id, so the 第一个 ACP prompt no longer inherits a dead handle. (#58669) Thanks @neeravmakwana",
      "ACPX/runtime: retry dead-session queue-owner repair without `--resume-session` when the reported ACPX session id is stale, so recovery still creates a fresh named session instead of failing session init. Thanks @obviyus.",
      "认证/OpenAI Codex: persist 插件-refreshed OAuth credentials to `认证-profiles.json` before returning them, so rotated Codex 刷新 tokens survive restart and 停止 falling into `refresh_token_reused` loops. (#53082)",
      "Discord/gateway: hand reconnect ownership back to Carbon, keep runtime status aligned with close/reconnect state, and force-stop sockets that open without reaching READY so Discord monitors recover promptly instead of waiting on stale health timeouts. (#59019) Thanks @obviyus",
      "配置/Telegram: migrate 移除d `channels.telegram.groupMentionsOnly` into `channels.telegram.groups[\"*\"].req界面reMention` on 加载 so legacy configs no longer crash at startup. (#55336) thanks @jameslcowan."
    ]
  }
