    "bugfixes": [
      "Slack: 停止 retry-driven duplicate replies when draft-finalization edits fail ambiguously, and 记录 configured allowlisted users/channels by readable name instead of raw IDs.",
      "Agents/OpenAI Responses: normalize raw bundled MCP 工具 schemas on the WebSocket/Responses 路径 so bare-object, object-ish, and 顶部-level union MCP tools no longer get rejected by OpenAI during 工具 registration. (#58299) Thanks @yelog.",
      "ACP/安全: 替换 ACP's dangerous-工具 name 覆盖 with semantic approval classes, so only narrow 只读 reads/searches can auto-approve while indirect exec-capable and 控制-plane tools always req界面re explicit prompt approval. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "ACP/sessions_spawn: 注册 ACP child runs for completion tracking and lifecycle cleanup, and make registration-failure cleanup explicitly best-effort so callers do not assume an already-started ACP turn was fully aborted. (#40885) Thanks @xaeon2026 and @vincentkoc.",
      "ACP/tasks: mark cleanly exited ACP runs as blocked when they 结束 on deterministic write or 授权 blockers, and wake the parent 会话 with a 关注-向上 instead of falsely reporting 成功.",
      "ACPX/runtime: derive the bundled ACPX expected 版本 from the extension package metadata instead of hardcoding a separate literal, so 插件-local ACPX installs 停止 drifting out of health-check parity after 版本 bumps. (#49089) Thanks @jiejiesks and @vincentkoc.",
      "Agents/Anthropic failover: treat Anthropic `API_error` payloads with `An unexpected 错误 occurred while 处理中 the response` as transient so retry/fallback can engage instead of surfacing a terminal failure. (#57441) Thanks @zijiess and @vincentkoc.",
      "Agents/compaction: keep late compaction-retry completions from double-resolving 完成 compaction futures, so interrupted or timed-out compactions 停止 surfacing spurious second-completion races. (#57796) Thanks @joshavant.",
      "Agents/禁用 providers: make 禁用 providers disappear from default model selection and embedded provider fallback, while letting explicitly pinned 禁用 providers fail with a 清除 配置 错误 instead of silently taking traffic. (#57735) Thanks @rileybrown-开发 and @vincentkoc.",
      "Agents/OAuth output: force exec-host OAuth output readers through the gateway fs policy so embedded gateway runs stop crashing when provider auth writes land outside the current sandbox workspace. (#58249) Thanks @joshavant.",
      "Agents/系统 prompt: 修复 `agent.name` interpolation in the embedded runtime 系统 prompt and make provider/model fallback text reflect the effective runtime selection after 开始. (#57625) Thanks @StllrSvr and @vincentkoc.",
      "Android/device 信息: read the 应用's 版本 metadata from the package manager instead of 隐藏 APIs so Android 15+ onboarding and device 信息 no longer fail to compile or 报告 占位符 values. (#58126) Thanks @L3ER0Y.",
      "Android/pairing: 停止 appending duplicate 推送 receiver entries to `gateway-服务.conf` on repeated QR pairing and keep 推送 registration bounded to the current successful pairing, so Android 推送 delivery stays healthy across re-pair and token rotation. (#58256) Thanks @surrealroad.",
      "应用 安装 smoke: 置顶 the 最新-发布 lookup to `最新`, cache the 第一个 稳定 安装 版本 across the rerun, and relax prerelease package assertions so the Parallels smoke lane can validate 稳定-to-main upgrades even when `测试` moves ahead or the guest starts from an older 稳定. (#58177) Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "认证/profiles: keep the 最后一个 successful 配置 加载 in memory for the running process and 刷新 that snapshot on successful writes/reloads, so hot paths 停止 reparsing `openclaw.json` between watcher-driven swaps.",
      "配置/SecretRef + 控制 界面: harden SecretRef redaction round-trip 恢复, block unsafe raw fallback (force 表单 模式 when raw is unavailable), and preflight submitted-配置 SecretRefs before 配置 write RPC persistence. (#58044) Thanks @joshavant.",
      "配置/Telegram: migrate 移除d `channels.telegram.groupMentionsOnly` into `channels.telegram.groups[\\\"*\\\"].req界面reMention` on 加载 so legacy configs no longer crash at startup. (#55336) thanks @jameslcowan.",
      "配置/更新: 停止 `openclaw doctor` write-backs from persisting 插件-injected channel defaults, so `openclaw 更新` no longer seeds 配置 keys that later 中断 服务 刷新 validation. (#56834) Thanks @openperf.",
      "Control 界面/agents: auto-load agent workspace files on initial Files panel open, and populate overview model/workspace/fallbacks from effective runtime agent metadata so defaulted models no longer show as `Not set`. (#56637) Thanks @dxsx84.",
      "控制 界面/slash commands: make `/steer` and `/redirect` work from the chat command palette with 可见 待处理 state for 激活-运行 `/steer`, 正确 redirected-运行 tracking, and a single canonical `/steer` entry in the command 菜单. (#54625) Thanks @fuller-stack-开发.",
      "Cron/announce: preserve all deliverable text payloads for announce 模式 instead of collapsing to the 最后一个 chunk, so multi-line cron reports deliver in full to Telegram forum topics.",
      "Cron/isolated sessions: carry the full live-session provider, model, and auth-profile selection across retry restarts so cron jobs with model overrides no longer fail or loop on mid-run model-switch requests. (#57972) Thanks @issaba1.",
      "Diffs/配置: preserve schema-shaped 插件 配置 parsing from `diffs插件ConfigSchema.safeParse()`, so direct callers keep `defaults` and `安全` sections instead of receiving flattened 工具 defaults. (#57904) Thanks @gumadeiras.",
      "Diffs: fall 返回 to plain text when `lang` hints are 无效 during diff render and viewer hydration, so bad or stale language values no longer 中断 the diff viewer. (#57902) Thanks @gumadeiras.",
      "Discord/voice: enforce the same g界面ld channel and member allowlist checks on spoken voice ingress before transcription, so joined voice channels no longer accept speech from users outside the configured Discord 访问 policy. Thanks @cyjhhh and @vincentkoc.",
      "Docker/setup: force B界面ldKit for local image b界面lds (including sandbox image b界面lds) so `./docker-setup.sh` no longer fails on `RUN --mount=...` when hosts default to Docker's legacy b界面lder. (#56681) Thanks @zhangh界面-china.",
      "Docs/anchors: 修复 broken English docs links and make Mint anchor audits run against the English-source docs tree. (#57039) thanks @velvet-shark.",
      "Doctor/插件s: 跳过 false Matrix legacy-helper warnings when no migration plans exist, and keep bundled `enabledByDefault` 插件s in the gateway startup set. (#57931) Thanks @dinakars777.",
      "Exec approvals/macOS: unwrap `arch` and `xcrun` before deriving shell payloads and 允许-always patterns, so wrapper approvals stay bound to the carried command instead of the outer carrier. Thanks @tdjackey and @vincentkoc.",
      "Exec approvals: unwrap `caffeinate` and `沙箱-exec` before persisting 允许-always trust so later shell payload changes still req界面re a fresh approval. Thanks @tdjackey and @vincentkoc.",
      "Exec/approvals: infer Discord and Telegram exec approvers from existing owner 配置 when `execApprovals.approvers` is unset, extend the default approval window to 30 minutes, and clarify approval-unavailable g界面dance so approvals do not appear to silently disappear.",
      "Pi/T界面: flush 消息-boundary replies at `message_end` so turns 停止 looking stuck until the 下一个 nudge when the 最终 reply was already 就绪. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Exec/approvals: keep `awk` and `sed` family binaries out of the low-risk `safeBins` fast 路径, and 停止 doctor profile scaffolding from treating them 点赞 ordinary custom filters. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Exec/env: block proxy, TLS, and Docker endpoint env overrides in host execution so request-scoped commands cannot silently reroute outbound traffic or trust attacker-supplied certificate settings. Thanks @AntAI安全Lab.",
      "Exec/env: block Python package index 覆盖 variables from request-scoped host exec 环境 sanitization so package fetches cannot be redirected through a caller-supplied index. Thanks @nexrin and @vincentkoc.",
      "Exec/node: 停止 gateway-side workdir fallback from rewriting explicit `host=node` cwd values to the gateway filesystem, so remote node exec approval and runs keep using the intended node-local 目录. (#50961) Thanks @openperf.",
      "Exec/runtime: default implicit exec to `host=auto`, resolve that target to sandbox only when a sandbox runtime exists, keep explicit `host=sandbox` fail-closed without sandbox, and show `/exec` effective host state in runtime status/docs.",
      "Exec: fail closed when the implicit 沙箱 host has no 沙箱 runtime, and 停止 denied async approval followups from reusing prior command 输出 from the same 会话. (#56800) Thanks @scoootscooob.",
      "Feishu/groups: keep quoted replies and topic bootstrap 上下文 aligned with group sender allowlists so only allowlisted thread messages seed agent 上下文. Thanks @AntAI安全Lab and @vincentkoc.",
      "Gateway/attachments: offload large inbound images without leaking `media://` markers into text-only runs, preserve mixed attachment order for model 输入框/transcripts, and fail closed when model 镜像 capability cannot be resolved. (#55513) Thanks @Syysean.",
      "Gateway/认证: keep shared-认证 rate limiting 激活 during WebSocket handshake attempts even when callers also send device-token candidates, so bogus device-token fields no longer suppress shared-secret brute-force tracking. Thanks @kexinoh and @vincentkoc.",
      "Gateway/认证: reject mismatched browser `Origin` headers on trusted-proxy HTTP operator requests while keeping origin-less headless proxy clients working. Thanks @AntAI安全Lab and @vincentkoc.",
      "Gateway/device tokens: 断开连接 激活 device sessions after token rotation so newly rotated credentials revoke existing live connections immediately instead of 等待中 for those sockets to 关闭 naturally. Thanks @zsxsoft and @vincentkoc.",
      "Gateway/health: carry webhook-vs-polling 账户 模式 from channel descriptors into runtime snapshots so passive channels 点赞 LINE and BlueBubbles 跳过 false stale-socket health failures. (#47488) Thanks @karesans界面-u.",
      "Gateway/pairing: 恢复 QR bootstrap onboarding handoff so fresh `/pair qr` iPhone setup can auto-approve the 初始 node pairing, receive a reusable node device token, and 停止 retrying with spent bootstrap 认证. (#58382) Thanks @ngutman.",
      "Gateway/OpenAI 兼容性: accept flat Responses API function 工具 definitions on `/v1/responses` and preserve `strict` when normalizing hosted tools into the embedded runner, so spec-compliant clients 点赞 Codex no longer fail validation or silently lose strict 工具 enforcement. Thanks @malaiwah and @vincentkoc.",
      "Gateway/OpenAI HTTP: 恢复 default operator scopes for bearer-authenticated requests that omit `x-openclaw-scopes`, so headless `/v1/chat/completions` and 会话-history callers work again after the recent method-scope hardening. (#57596) Thanks @openperf.",
      "Gateway/插件s: scope 插件-认证 HTTP route runtime clients to read-only 访问 and keep gateway-authenticated 插件 routes on write scope, so 插件-owned webhook handlers do not inherit write-capable runtime 访问 by default. Thanks @davidluzsilva and @vincentkoc.",
      "Gateway/SecretRef: resolve restart token drift checks with merged 服务/runtime env sources and hard-fail un支持ed mutable SecretRef plus OAuth-profile combinations so restart warnings and policy enforcement match runtime behavior. (#58141) Thanks @joshavant.",
      "Gateway/tools HTTP: tighten HTTP 工具-invoke 授权 so owner-only tools stay off HTTP invoke paths. (#57773) Thanks @jacobtomlinson.",
      "Harden async approval followup delivery in webchat-only sessions (#57359) Thanks @joshavant.",
      "Heartbeat/认证: 防止 exec-event heartbeat runs from inheriting owner-only 工具 访问 from the 会话 delivery target, so node exec 输出 stays on the non-owner 工具 surface even when the target 会话 belongs to the owner. Thanks @AntAI安全Lab and @vincentkoc.",
      "Hooks/配置: accept runtime channel 插件 ids in `hooks.mappings[].channel` (for example `feishu`) instead of rejecting non-core channels during 配置 validation. (#56226) Thanks @AiKrai001.",
      "Hooks/会话 routing: rebind hook-triggered `agent:` 会话 keys to the actual target agent before isolated dispatch so dedicated hook agents keep their own 会话-scoped 工具 and 插件 identity. Thanks @kexinoh and @vincentkoc.",
      "Host exec/env: block 添加itional request-scoped env overrides that can redirect Docker endpoints, trust roots, compiler include paths, package resolution, or Python 环境 roots during approved host runs. Thanks @tdjackey and @vincentkoc.",
      "镜像 generation/b界面ld: write 稳定 runtime alias files into `dist/` and route provider-认证 runtime lookups through those aliases so 镜像-generation providers keep resolving 认证/runtime modules after reb界面lds instead of crashing on missing hashed chunk files.",
      "iOS/Live Activities: mark the `ActivityKit` import in `LiveActivityManager.swift` as `@preconcurrency` so Xcode 26.4 / Swift 6 b界面lds 停止 failing on strict concurrency checks. (#57180) Thanks @ngutman.",
      "LINE/ACP: 添加 current-conversation binding and inbound binding-routing parity so `/acp spawn ... --thread here`, configured ACP bindings, and 激活 conversation-bound ACP sessions work on LINE 点赞 the other conversation channels.",
      "LINE/markdown: preserve underscores inside Latin, Cyrillic, and CJK words when stripping markdown, while still removing standalone `_italic_` markers on the shared text-runtime 路径 used by LINE and TTS. (#47465) Thanks @jackjin1997.",
      "Agents/failover: make overloaded same-provider retry count and retry delay configurable via `认证.cooldowns`, default to one retry with no delay, and document the model-fallback behavior."
    ]
  }
},
  {
  "version": "2026.3.31-beta.1",
