      "Tasks: 添加 a minimal SQLite-backed task flow registry plus task-to-flow linkage scaffolding, so orchestrated work can 开始 gaining a 第一个-class parent record without changing current task delivery behavior. Thanks @mbelinky and @vincentkoc.",
      "Tasks: persist blocked state on one-task task flows and let the same flow reopen cleanly on retry, so blocked detached work can carry a parent-level reason and 继续 without fragmenting into a 新增 job. Thanks @mbelinky and @vincentkoc.",
      "Tasks: route one-task ACP and subagent 更新s through a parent task-flow owner 上下文, so detached work can emerge 返回 through the intended parent thread/会话 instead of speaking only as a raw child task. Thanks @mbelinky and @vincentkoc.",
      "LINE/outbound media: 添加 LINE 镜像, video, and audio outbound sends on the LINE-specific delivery 路径, including explicit 预览/tracking handling for videos while keeping generic media sends on the existing 镜像-only route. (#45826) Thanks @masatohoshino.",
      "Matrix/history: 添加 可选 room history 上下文 for Matrix group triggers via `channels.matrix.historyLimit`, with per-agent watermarks and retry-safe snapshots so failed trigger retries do not drift into newer room messages. (#57022) thanks @chain710.",
      "Matrix/network: 添加 explicit `channels.matrix.proxy` config for routing Matrix traffic through an HTTP(S) proxy, including account-level overrides and matching probe/runtime behavior. (#56931) thanks @patrick-yingxi-pan.",
      "Matrix/streaming: 添加 draft streaming so partial Matrix replies 更新 the same message in place instead of sending a new message for each chunk. (#56387) Thanks @jrusz.",
      "Matrix/threads: 添加 per-DM `threadReplies` overrides and keep thread 会话 isolation aligned with the effective room or DM thread policy from the triggering 消息 onward. (#57995) thanks @teconomix.",
      "MCP: 添加 remote HTTP/SSE 服务器 支持 for `mcp.servers` 链接 configs, including 认证 headers and safer 配置 redaction for MCP credentials. (#50396) Thanks @dhananjai1729.",
      "Memory/QMD: 添加 per-agent `memorySearch.qmd.extraCollections` so agents can opt into cross-agent 会话 搜索 without flattening every transcript collection into one shared QMD namespace. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Microsoft Teams/member 信息: 添加 a Graph-backed member 信息 action so Teams automations and tools can resolve channel member details directly from Microsoft Graph. (#57528) Thanks @sudie-codes.",
      "Nostr/inbound DMs: verify inbound event signatures before pairing or sender-授权 side effects, so forged DM events no longer 创建 pairing requests or trigger reply attempts. Thanks @smaeljaish771 and @vincentkoc.",
      "OpenAI/Responses: 前进 configured `text.verbosity` across Responses HTTP and WebSocket transports, surface it in `/状态`, and keep per-agent verbosity precedence aligned with runtime behavior. (#47106) Thanks @merc1305 and @vincentkoc.",
      "Pi/Codex: 添加 native Codex web 搜索 支持 for embedded Pi runs, including 配置/docs/wizard coverage and managed-工具 suppression when native Codex 搜索 is 激活. (#46579) Thanks @Evizero.",
      "Slack/exec approvals: 添加 native Slack approval routing and approver 授权 so exec approval prompts can stay in Slack instead of falling 返回 to the Web 界面 or terminal. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "TTS: 添加 structured provider diagnostics and fallback attempt analytics. (#57954) Thanks @joshavant.",
      "WhatsApp/reactions: agents can now react with emoji on incoming WhatsApp messages, enabling more natural conversational interactions 点赞 acknowledging a photo with ❤️ instead of typing a reply. Thanks @mcaxtr.",
      "Agents/BTW: force `/btw` side questions to 禁用 provider reasoning so Anthropic adaptive-thinking sessions 停止 failing with `No BTW response generated`. 修复es #55376. Thanks @Catteres and @vincentkoc.",
      "CLI/onboarding: 重置 the remote gateway 链接 prompt to the safe loopback default after declining a discovered endpoint, so onboarding does not keep a previously rejected remote 链接. (#57828)",
      "Agents/exec defaults: honor per-agent `tools.exec` defaults when no inline directive or 会话 覆盖 is present, so configured exec host, 安全, ask, and node settings actually apply. (#57689)",
      "沙箱/networking: sanitize SSH subprocess env vars through the shared 沙箱 policy and route marketplace 归档 downloads plus Ollama discovery, 认证, and pull requests through the guarded fetch 路径 so sandboxed execution and remote fetches 关注 the repo's trust boundaries. (#57848, #57850)"
