      "Agents/Anthropic failover: treat Anthropic `API_error` payloads with `An unexpected 错误 occurred while 处理中 the response` as transient so retry/fallback can engage instead of surfacing a terminal failure. (#57441) Thanks @zijiess and @vincentkoc.",
      "Agents/compaction: keep late compaction-retry rejections handled after the aggregate timeout 路径 wins without swallowing real pre-timeout wait failures, so timed-out retries no longer surface an unhandled rejection on later 取消订阅. (#57451) Thanks @mpz4life and @vincentkoc.",
      "Agents/上下文 pruning: count supplementary-plane CJK characters with the shared code-point-aware estimator so 上下文 pruning stops underestimating Japanese and Chinese text that uses Extension B ideographs. (#39985) Thanks @Edward-Qiang-2024.",
