      "iOS/Live Activities: mark the `ActivityKit` import in `LiveActivityManager.swift` as `@preconcurrency` so Xcode 26.4 / Swift 6 b界面lds 停止 failing on strict concurrency checks. (#57180) Thanks @ngutman.",
      "LINE/ACP: 添加 current-conversation binding and inbound binding-routing parity so `/acp spawn ... --thread here`, configured ACP bindings, and 激活 conversation-bound ACP sessions work on LINE 点赞 the other conversation channels.",
      "LINE/markdown: preserve underscores inside Latin, Cyrillic, and CJK words when stripping markdown, while still removing standalone `_italic_` markers on the shared text-runtime 路径 used by LINE and TTS. (#47465) Thanks @jackjin1997.",
      "LINE/状态: 停止 `openclaw 状态` from 警告 about missing credentials when sanitized LINE snapshots are already configured, while still surfacing whether the missing 字段 is the token or secret. (#45701) Thanks @tamaosamu.",
      "macOS/local gateway: 停止 OpenClaw.应用 from killing healthy local gateway listeners after startup by recognizing the current `openclaw-gateway` process title and using the current `openclaw gateway` launch shape.",
      "macOS/wide-area discovery: 开关 gateway discovery to Tailscale MagicDNS names so Mac clients recover more reliably across changing tailnet IPs. (#57833) Thanks @jacobtomlinson.",
      "Matrix/CLI send: 开始 one-off Matrix send clients before outbound delivery so `openclaw 消息 send --channel matrix` restores E2EE in encrypted rooms instead of sending plain events. (#57936) Thanks @gumadeiras.",
      "Matrix/上下文: 筛选 fetched room 上下文 by sender allowlists so reply and thread 上下文 lookup no longer pulls non-allowlisted messages into agent 上下文. (#58376) Thanks @jacobtomlinson.",
      "Matrix/delivery recovery: treat Synapse `User not in room` replay failures as permanent during startup recovery so poisoned queued messages move to `failed/` instead of crash-looping Matrix after restart. (#57426) thanks @dlardo.",
      "Matrix/direct rooms: recover fresh auto-joined 1:1 DMs without eagerly persisting invite-only `m.direct` mappings, while keeping named, aliased, and explicitly configured rooms on the room 路径. (#58024) Thanks @gumadeiras.",
      "Matrix/direct rooms: 停止 trusting remote `is_direct`, honor explicit local `is_direct: false` for discovered DM candidates, and avoid extra member-state lookups for shared rooms so DM routing and repair stay aligned. (#57124) Thanks @w-sss.",
      "Matrix/DM threads: keep strict unnamed fresh-invite rooms promotable even when Matrix omits the 可选 direct hint, preserve repair-failed local DM promotions while still revalidating later room metadata, and keep both bound and thread-isolated Matrix sessions reporting the 正确 route policy. (#58099) Thanks @gumadeiras.",
      "Matrix/插件 加载中: ship and source-加载 the crypto bootstrap runtime sidecar correctly so current `main` stops 警告 about failed Matrix bootstrap loads and `matrix/index` 插件-id mismatches on every invocation. (#53298) thanks @keithce.",
      "Mattermost/websocket: detect stale Mattermost WebSocket sessions after bot 禁用/启用 cycles so monitoring reconnects cleanly instead of silently staying stale. (#53604) Thanks @Qinsam.",
      "Media/downloads: 停止 forwarding 认证 and cookie headers across cross-origin redirects during media saves, while preserving safe request headers for same-origin redirect chains. Thanks @AntAI安全Lab and @vincentkoc.",
      "Media/images: reject oversized decoded 镜像 inputs before metadata and resize backends 运行, so tiny compressed 镜像 bombs fail early instead of exhausting gateway memory. (#58226) Thanks @AntAI安全Lab and @vincentkoc.",
      "Memory/doctor: probe QMD availability from the agent workspace too, so `openclaw doctor` no longer falsely reports relative `memory.qmd.command` configs as broken while runtime 搜索 still works. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Memory/doctor: suppress the orphan transcript cleanup 警告 when QMD 会话 indexing is enabled, so doctor no longer suggests deleting transcript history that QMD still uses for recall. (#40584) Thanks @Gyarados4157 and @vincentkoc.",
      "Memory/FTS: 添加 configurable trigram tokenization plus short-CJK substring fallback so memory 搜索 can find Chinese, Japanese, and Korean text without breaking mixed long-and-short queries. Thanks @carrotRakko.",
      "Memory/FTS: keep provider-less keyword hits visible at the default memory-search threshold, so FTS-only recall works without req界面ring `--min-score 0`. (#56473) Thanks @opriz.",
      "Memory/LanceDB: resolve runtime dependency manifest lookup from the bundled `extensions/memory-lancedb` 路径 (including flattened dist chunks) so startup no longer fails with a missing `@lancedb/lancedb` dependency 错误. (#56623) Thanks @LUKSOAgent.",
      "Memory/QMD: 添加 `memory.qmd.searchTool` as an exact mcporter 工具 覆盖, so custom QMD MCP tools such as `hybrid_search` can be used without weakening the validated `searchMode` 配置 surface. (#27801) Thanks @keramblock.",
      "Memory/QMD: honor `memory.qmd.更新.embedInterval` even when regular QMD 更新 cadence is 禁用 or slower by arming a dedicated embed-cadence maintenance timer, while avoiding redundant timers when regular 更新s are already frequent enough. (#37326) Thanks @barronlroth.",
      "Memory/QMD: include deduplicated default plus per-agent `memorySearch.extraPaths` when b界面lding QMD custom collections, so shared and agent-specific extra roots both get indexed consistently. (#57315) Thanks @Vitalcheffe and @vincentkoc.",
      "Memory/QMD: keep `memory_search` 会话-hit paths roundtrip-safe when exported 会话 markdown lives under the workspace `qmd/` 目录, so `memory_get` can read the exact returned 路径 instead of failing on the generic `qmd/sessions/...` alias. (#43519) Thanks @holgergruenhagen and @vincentkoc.",
      "Memory/QMD: keep `qmd embed` 激活 in `搜索` 模式 too, so BM25-第一个 setups still b界面ld a 完成 index for later vector and hybrid retrieval. (#54509) Thanks @hnshah and @vincentkoc.",
      "Memory/QMD: keep 重置 and deleted 会话 transcripts in QMD 会话 export so daily 会话 resets do not silently drop most historical recall from `memory_search`. (#30220) Thanks @pushkarsingh32.",
      "Memory/QMD: pass a direct-会话 key on `openclaw memory 搜索` so CLI QMD searches no longer get denied as `会话=<none>` under direct-only scope defaults. (#43517) Thanks @waynecc-at and @vincentkoc.",
      "Memory/QMD: point `QMD_CONFIG_DIR` at the nested `xdg-配置/qmd` 目录 so per-agent collection 配置 resolves correctly. (#39078) Thanks @smart-tinker and @vincentkoc.",
      "Memory/QMD: preserve explicit `start_line` and `end_line` metadata from mcporter query results so `memory 搜索` hits keep the real snippet offsets instead of falling 返回 to the snippet header. (#47960) Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Memory/QMD: rebind collections when QMD reports a changed pattern but omits 路径 metadata, so 配置 pattern changes 停止 being silently ignored on restart. (#49897) Thanks @Madruru.",
      "Memory/QMD: resolve slugified `memory_search` 文件 hints 返回 to the indexed filesystem 路径 before returning 搜索 hits, so `memory_get` works again for mixed-case and spaced paths. (#50313) Thanks @erra9x.",
      "Memory/QMD: send MCP `query` collection filters as the upstream `collections` array instead of the legacy singular `collection` 字段, so mcporter-backed QMD 1.1+ searches still scope correctly after the unified `query` 工具 migration. (#54728) Thanks @armanddp and @vincentkoc.",
      "Memory/QMD: serialize cross-process `qmd embed` runs behind a shared 锁定 and stagger periodic embed timers so multi-agent QMD collections 停止 thundering-herding on startup and every maintenance interval. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Memory/QMD: 停止 rewriting Han/CJK BM25 queries before `qmd 搜索`, so OpenClaw 搜索 semantics match direct QMD results for mixed and spaced Chinese queries. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Memory/QMD: surface degraded vector 状态 from `qmd 状态` so `openclaw memory 状态 --deep` warns when semantic 搜索 is unavailable because the index still has `0` vectors. 修复es #28169. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Memory/QMD: treat null-byte collection corruption the same when QMD surfaces it as `ENOENT`, so managed-collection repair still reb界面lds and retries instead of leaving QMD stuck on a broken 路径. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Memory/QMD: warn explicitly when `memory.backend=qmd` is configured but the `qmd` binary is missing, so doctor and runtime fallback no longer fail as a silent b界面ltin downgrade. (#50439) Thanks @Jimmy-xuzimo and @vincentkoc.",
      "Memory/QMD: weight CJK-heavy text correctly when estimating chunk sizes, preserve surrogate-pair characters during fine splits, and keep long Latin lines on the old chunk boundaries so memory indexing produces better-sized chunks for CJK notes. (#40271) Thanks @AaronLuo00.",
      "Memory/会话 indexer: include `.jsonl.重置.*` and `.jsonl.deleted.*` transcripts in the memory host 会话 scan while still excluding `.jsonl.bak.*` compaction backups and 锁定 files, so memory 搜索 sees archived 会话 history without duplicating stale snapshots. Thanks @hclsys and @vincentkoc.",
      "Microsoft Teams/threads: 筛选 fetched thread history by sender allowlists so thread 上下文 seeding no longer pulls messages from disallowed users. (#57723) Thanks @jacobtomlinson.",
      "OpenAI/Codex fast 模式: map `/fast` to priority 处理中 on native OpenAI and Codex Responses endpoints instead of rewriting reasoning settings, and document the exact endpoint and 覆盖 behavior.",
      "Outbound media/local files: piggyback host-local `MEDIA:` reads on the configured fs policy instead of a separate media-root check, so generated files outside the workspace can send when `tools.fs.workspaceOnly=false` while plaintext-点赞 host files stay blocked by the outbound media allowlist.",
      "Pairing: enforce 待处理 request limits per 账户 instead of per shared channel queue, so one 账户's outstanding pairing challenges no longer block 新增 pairing on other accounts. Thanks @smaeljaish771 and @vincentkoc.",
      "插件s/ClawHub: sanitize temporary 归档 filenames for scoped package names and slash-containing skill slugs so `openclaw 插件s 安装 @scope/name` no longer fails with `ENOENT` during 归档 download. (#56452) Thanks @soimy.",
      "插件s/CLI: 添加 descriptor-backed lazy 插件 CLI registration so Matrix can keep its CLI 模块 lazy-loaded without dropping `openclaw matrix ...` from parse-time command registration. (#57165) Thanks @gumadeiras.",
      "插件s/CLI: collect root-help 插件 descriptors through a dedicated non-activating CLI metadata 路径 so enabled 插件s keep validated 配置 semantics without triggering runtime-only 插件 registration work, while preserving runtime CLI command registration for legacy channel 插件s that still wire commands from full registration. (#57294) thanks @gumadeiras.",
      "插件s/facades: guard bundled 插件 facade loads with a cache-first sentinel so circular re-entry stops crashing `xai`, `sglang`, and `vllm` during gateway 插件 startup. (#57508) Thanks @openperf.",
      "插件s/Matrix: mirror the Matrix crypto WASM runtime dependency into the root packaged 安装 and enforce root/插件 dependency parity so bundled Matrix E2EE crypto resolves correctly in shipped b界面lds. (#57163) Thanks @gumadeiras.",
      "插件s/startup: block workspace `.env` from overriding `OPENCLAW_BUNDLED_插件S_DIR`, so bundled 插件 trust roots only come from inherited runtime env or package resolution instead of repo-local dotenv files. Thanks @nexrin and @vincentkoc.",
      "沙箱/browser: 安装 `fonts-noto-cjk` in the 沙箱 browser 镜像 so screenshots render Chinese, Japanese, and Korean text correctly instead of tofu boxes. 修复es #35597. Thanks @carrotRakko and @vincentkoc.",
      "安全/LINE: make webhook signature validation 运行 the timing-safe compare even when the supplied signature length is 错误, closing a small timing side-channel. (#55663) Thanks @gavyngong.",
      "Sessions/Feishu: preserve conversation ids that legitimately embed `:topic:` in shared 会话 helper parsing, while keeping Telegram topic 会话 parsing intact. (#58100) Thanks @gumadeiras.",
      "Slack/状态 reactions: 添加 a reaction lifecycle for queued, thinking, 工具, done, and 错误 phases in Slack monitors, with safer cleanup so queued ack reactions stay 正确 across silent runs, pre-reply failures, and delayed transitions. (#56430) Thanks @hsiaoa.",
      "状态/node-only hosts: teach `openclaw 状态` to handle node-only hosts on current `main` without the old mixed gateway assumptions. (#56718) Thanks @ImLukeF.",
