      "T界面/chat: keep optimistic outbound 用户 messages 可见 during 激活 runs by deferring local-运行 binding until the 第一个 gateway chat event reveals the real 运行 id, preventing premature history reloads from wiping 待处理 local sends. (#54722) Thanks @seanturner001.",
      "T界面/model picker: keep searchable `/model` and `/models` 输入框 模式 from hijacking `j`/`k` as navigation keys, and harden 宽度 bounds under `m`-filtered model lists so 搜索 no longer crashes on long rows. (#30156) Thanks @briannicholls.",
