      "SSH 沙箱/upload: reject workspace symlinks that resolve outside the uploaded tree before syncing to the remote 沙箱, so later agent writes cannot be redirected through escaped links. Thanks @AntAI安全Lab and @vincentkoc.",
      "Slack/interactive replies: resolve Slack Block Kit reply delivery from both authored `channelData.slack.blocks` payloads and directive-generated interactive replies, and keep Slack 按钮 styles mapped onto 有效 Block Kit 按钮 rendering so interactive replies 停止 dropping on Slack-specific delivery paths. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Subagents/announcements: preserve the requester agent id for inline deterministic 工具 spawns so named agents without channel bindings can still announce completions through the 正确 owner 会话. (#55437) Thanks @kAIborg24.",
      "Telegram/Anthropic streaming: replace raw invalid stream-order provider errors with a safe retry message so internal `message_start/message_stop` failures do not leak into chats. (#55408) Thanks @imydal.",
      "Tlon/media: route inbound 镜像 downloads through the shared media store, cap each download at 6 MB, and 停止 after 8 images per 消息 so large Tlon posts no longer balloon local media storage. Thanks @AntAI安全Lab and @vincentkoc.",
      "Agents/live 开关: 停止 transient cron and subagent model overrides from being misread as persisted live-会话 switches, so isolated runs no longer fail with `LiveSessionModelSwitchError`. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "Agents/工具-call repair: recover malformed Kimi/OpenRouter 工具-call argument streams when provider preambles appear before JSON payloads, and fail closed on non-工具 leading text so fragment strings do not leak into filesystem 路径 arguments during sub-agent runs. (#56560) Thanks @Originalwhite.",
      "Gateway/startup: keep configured primary-model warmup on the static model 路径 so 容器 boots do not snapshot-加载 provider runtime graphs just to validate a configured model. Thanks @vincentkoc.",
      "OpenAI/Responses: omit disabled reasoning payloads across OpenAI, Codex, and Azure OpenAI request b界面lders so GPT-5 endpoints no longer reject `reasoning.effort: \"none\"`. (#58208) Thanks @jalehman.",
      "WhatsApp/outbound: restore runtime send/action routing and outbound 兼容性 after the recent channel seam 重构 so outbound sends, reactions, and related media actions keep reaching the active session.",
      "xAI/Responses: normalize 镜像-bearing 工具 results for xAI responses payloads, including OpenResponses-style `input_image.source` parts, so 镜像 工具 replays no longer 422 on the 关注-向上 turn. (#58017) Thanks @neeravmakwana.",
      "Zalo/webhooks: scope replay dedupe to the authenticated target so one configured 账户 can no longer cause same-id inbound events for another target to be dropped. Thanks @smaeljaish771 and @vincentkoc.",
      "插件s/prompt b界面ld: preserve the highest-priority `systemPrompt` when merging `before_prompt_b界面ld` hook results instead of letting lower-priority hooks overwrite it. (#58375)",
      "Tlon/settings migration: preserve explicit empty-array settings during migration so restart-time reseeding no longer restores older file-config values. (#58370)",
      "插件s/marketplace: harden marketplace 归档 installs by surfacing guarded download failures as structured 安装 errors and deriving temp filenames from the 最终 resolved 链接. (#58267)",
      "界面/DOM safety: b界面ld the chat delete-confirm popover and Canvas Host fallback status line with DOM nodes instead of injected HTML strings. (#58269, #58266)",
      "Media/文件 handling: 创建 镜像 temp work directories under the shared OpenClaw temp root and 停止 widening allowed local media roots from reply or 工具 source paths, keeping local media 访问 limited to configured and agent-scoped roots. (#58270, #57770)",
      "Telegram/安全: migrate legacy pairing `allowFrom` state to the `default` 账户 only and gate group voice-消息 preflight transcription on sender 授权 so unauthorized senders cannot trigger paid transcription before being dropped. (#58165, #57566)",
      "Exec approvals: 停止 shell init-文件 flags from matching persisted script-路径 approvals, detect command-carrier inline eval in tools 点赞 `awk`, `find`, `xargs`, `make`, and `sed`, and treat the awk family as interpreter-点赞 so 允许-always decisions no longer persist interpreter paths. (#58369, #57842, #57772)",
      "Voice call/Telnyx: canonicalize verified webhook signatures before deriving replay keys so eq界面valent Base64 and Base64URL encodings dedupe correctly. (#57829)",
      "Gateway/HTTP trust boundaries: 忽略 self-declared bearer scopes, deny dangerous HTTP 工具-invoke paths by default, req界面re write scope on `/v1/embeddings`, and 绑定 OpenAI-compatible `/v1/chat/completions` plus `/v1/responses` ingress as non-owner so external HTTP callers cannot self-upgrade 访问. (#57783, #57771, #57721, #57769, #57778)",
      "Gateway/trusted config and bootstrap: clear self-declared scopes for device-less `trusted-proxy` WebSocket connects and trim the Control 界面 bootstrap payload to only the fields needed before the normal handshake. (#57692, #57727)",
      "Skills and workspace safety: replace raw skill-file reads with a symlink-safe, root-confined loader and pin workspace-only `apply_patch` delete and directory-creation mutations to verified workspace roots so path rebind races fail closed. (#57519, #56016)",
      "Env and filesystem hardening: block credential and gateway 认证 env vars from workspace `.env` files, always strip dangerous inherited host env vars such as `BROWSER` and `GIT_EDITOR`, and keep sensitive host paths and OpenClaw state roots blocked even when external 沙箱 绑定 sources are allowed. (#57767, #57559, #56024)",
      "OpenShell and ACP 文件 boundaries: 跳过 symlinks and preserve trusted host-only directories during OpenShell mirror sync, and route ACP attachment reads through the shared attachment cache so local files outside allowed roots are no longer forwarded. (#57693, #57690)",
      "Channel/webhook 授权: 跳过 Discord audio preflight transcription for unauthorized g界面ld senders, 添加 a shared pre-认证 in-flight guard to Synology Chat webhooks, and validate Microsoft Teams bearer 认证 before JSON body parsing. (#57695, #57722, #57686)",
      "Infra/randomness: 替换 `Math.random()` in affected identifier and delay-jitter paths with shared secure-random helpers, including 界面 U界面D generation. (#57744)"
    ]
  }
